insert  into `daily_fire`(`id`,`image`,`edition`,`date`,`title`,`full_text`,`dateposted`) values (1,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-01','Our Focus GOD WILL TOUCH WHATEVER YOU COUNT ON ','DAY: SUN 1st April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 32:32 \"because he touched the hollow of Jacob \'s thigh in the sinew that shrank. â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus GOD WILL TOUCH WHATEVER YOU COUNT 0N . \r\n\r\nThe thigh is usually the part the body relies on. God touched the thigh of Jacob so he could learn never to depend on himself. Our God does the same today, whatever or whoever you depend on besides God, he will surely touch. God does not want us to depend on anyone besides him. He wants us to solely rely on him. It is dangerous to rely on anything else besides God. For God will not take it light with whatever you rely on besides him. I admonish you today, never to put your trust on anyone/anything besides God. Whoever you know can fail, only God can be there for us for life, why not count on him today? See how many people have failed you in time past why not depend on him to provide whatever help you need. He is more than able to do it for you just count on him . \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father; touch anything I \'m trying to count on. let me only depend on you. Take away whatever is striving to take my heart away from you that you may be my only hope. help me never to doubt your plans for my life. Let me trust you no matter what I go through(Amen). \r\n(God will cut down whatever you count on besides him)\r\nOther text: Ps. 14:3-5 for your reading.','2018-05-19 17:41:15'),(2,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-02','Our Focus: RISING UP EARLY TO BLESS ','DAY: MON 2nd April., 2018 \r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 31 :55 \"And early in the morning Laban rose up, and kissed his sons and his daughters, and blessed them,and Laban departed, and returned unto his place. â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: RISING UP EARLY TO BLESS \r\n\r\nWhat do you say to your family as you wake up every morning? Some parent wake up with rain of curses on their household, they discharge terrible abuses on their children \"you this stupid boy\" oloshi oloriburuku \"onyioshi onyayara\" â€œdaniska yaro\" oh what a bad way to start the day for your children! As Refiner\'s member we must never start our day with curses. Don\'t destroy the day for your family. What you say early in the morning is very powerful, it controls the rest of the day! Lets learn to start each day on a blessing note for our house. Bless your children each morning just say few words like \"you are blessed, you shall be wonderful children, no devil can destroy you for me. You shall be a special child to your generations\" words like this will make a wonderful day for your children. Don\'t wake them with curses. Bless them early in the morning as you pray and our children will be successful in life in Jesus name.\r\n(Your words are like waters on plant.blessing on your lips is like cold water on a tender plant while curses are like hot water on a plant. Bless your children to success)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, grant me the grace to bless my household every morning, let me never say evil â€˜ to them that it may be well with them, for every time I\'ve said something evil to them, Father I retract those words and release blessings on them. Let people see great potential in my household, my children will bring honor and not disgrace to this family  in Jesus name. \r\n\r\nOther text: Esther 10:3 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-19 17:43:41'),(3,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-03','Our Focus: GOD\'S GLORY WILL RISE ON YOU ','DAY: TUES 3rd April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 32:31 \"Abraham! as he passed over Penuel the sun rose upon him \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: GOD\'S GLORY WILL RISE ON YOU \r\n\r\nAs the sun rises all eyes see her shining so shall God\'s glory rise upon you. When God\'s glory rises upon you, you will suddenly become noticeable to everyone around you. When his glory rises upon you, you become unbeatable by any competitor. God\'s glory beautifies our lives. It makes us different from others. That glory is rising upon us from today. Whenever the sun rises people come out en-mass to its attraction to carry out their duties. God\'s glory is rising upon this ministry, many will be attracted to it. People shall flock to this ministry as they behold the glory of God shining upon our lives. I want to conclude by saying as the sun exposes harmful objects so shall the glory of God on us exposes every satanic device among us. There is no hiding place for the devil with God\'s glory on us, I congratulate you for the rising of his glory upon us All! \r\n(Godâ€™s glory has the power to change your story)\r\nOur Prayer: Thank you father for your great intention to put  your glory on me and my family, Lord, let your glory keep rising and shining upon us that your beauty may be seen on us all. Let your glory lead us to a life full of righteousness and keep us safe at all times. Let your glory expose every satanic operation in our midst that we may live a victorious life in Jesus name. \r\n\r\nOther text: Isa 60:1-6 for your reading\r\n','2018-05-19 17:44:32'),(4,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-04','Our Focus: YOU SHALL SEE THE LORD TODAY ','DAY: WED 4th April., 2018 \r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 32:30 â€And Jacob called the name of the place Peniel;  for I have seen God face to face, and my life is preserved. \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU SHALL SEE THE LORD TODAY \r\n\r\nYou shall see the: lord today how? Whenever you see favour, miracle and blessings you have seen the Lord face to face. God face is favour his voice is wonders and his hands is full of blessing Get set to experience his favour today, you shall see his wonders and you shall receive his blessings then you will conclude this weekend you have seen God face to face. Evil will never touch you, when you see him, sickness must disappear. As you see him. Your business must flourish and you must never be down. Today, shall be a wonderful day. For you shall see proof of his presence, Favour, wonders and blessing so be it in Jesus name! \r\n(Godâ€™s face transmit favour on His children, seeing His face is to obtain favour)\r\nOur Prayer: Lord, cause me to see you today as I go out, let your favour, wonder and blessing be revealed to me on every side, direct me to where I will experience your exceptional favour, every step I take I will see you, everything I touch today must exhibit favour and blessings, I will not see the devil in my way today, I am covered in the name of Jesus Christ!\r\n\r\nOther text: Isa. 33:16-17 for your Reading. \r\n','2018-05-19 17:45:52'),(5,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-05',' Focus: GOD WILL CHANGE SOMETHING ABOUT YOU ','DAY: THURS 5th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 32:27-28 â€And he said unto him, what is thy name? And he said Jacob. And he said, thy name shall be called no more Jacob, but Israel; for as a prince has! thou power with God and with men, and hast prevailed\".\r\n\r\nFocus: GOD WILL CHANGE SOMETHING ABOUT YOU \r\n\r\nAs for Jacob his name was changed to Israel. Yours may not be a change of name but a circumstance. All I know today is that the Lord will change something about your life. Whatever is not alright or accurate in your life I command a mysterious change for you in the name of Jesus Christ. Are you sick? You need a change to health. Are you facing depression? You need a change to impression. Are you jobless? My God will give you a change to Employed, Are you barren? God is making you a mother today, Are you single?  You are meeting your spouse today, Are you worried and dejected? My God will give you a change to happiness and glory, you will experience a definite change in your life today. A gift will come your way today that will LIFT you to a new realm of favour, that is a change. I command change for good for you today in the name of Jesus Christ! \r\n(Positive change is moving out of bitterness to betterness. That will be your experience!\r\nOur Prayer: Today, lord change something about me. Let your happiness replace my heaviness. Whatever has been causing pain and dissatisfaction in my life, Lord change it for me today. Let me have cause to celebrate, I declare the loss of every terrible and painful situations in my life, I shall face them no more, Let me have a different and better experience of your favour as I go out today... (Amen). \r\n\r\nOther text: Isa 55:12-13 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 17:49:25'),(6,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-06',' Our Focus: DON \'T GIVE UP UNTIL YOU GET WHAT YOU NEED ','DAY: FRI 6th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 32:26 \"And he said, let me go, for the day breaketh, and he said, I will not let thee go except thou bless me\"\r\n\r\nOur Focus: DON \'T GIVE UP UNTIL YOU GET WHAT YOU NEED \r\n\r\nPersistence is a powerful key to victory in life. If you easily give up you will rarely get what you need in life. Nothing great comes at the first approach, strike again to cross the border to success. People who easily give up don\'t get up. The proof of your desire for a favour is to persist in your request for it until you have it. Sometime the person you are asking for a favour may not want to give you-easily but your persistence can enforce you to have it. That proves your seriousness. Jacob persisted until he got the blessing. May you never give up in your pursuits until you get it, in the name of the Lord you will get your desire! Can I hear your Amen! \r\n(whatever you desire, pursue until you get it, disregard the cross for the crown)\r\nOur Prayer: Daddy, give me the grace to persist in my request until it is granted. Give me a heart of patience, perseverance and persistence along with courage to hold on till my desires are granted. Let me never give up too easily. Let me hold tight until the rain of favour falls, I will not lose my blessing due to laxity in Jesus name (Amen). \r\n\r\nOther text: Luke 1 8:1 -8 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-19 17:52:10'),(7,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-07','Our Focus: ARE YOU LEFT ALONE? ','\r\nDAY: SAT 7th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 32:24 â€œAnd Jacob was left alone; and there wrestled a man with him until the breaking of the day.â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: ARE YOU LEFT ALONE? \r\n\r\nSome time when you are left alone it could be Godâ€™s arrangement to secure your personal attention. If you seem to be alone, God might want to speak with you if you listen carefully you will hear his voice within you. He will discuss vital issues about your life with you. People may not always be around you, there will be time to be alone so you can hear from above. So donâ€™t hate being alone sometime. Your brain works better sometime when alone, you think deeper and receive divine ideas better so there could be blessing in your lonely moment. When you are getting too distracted God can arrange circumstances where people withdraw from you, so he could get your attention. Beloved, maximize your lonely moment, interact with heaven and receive profound ideas. \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Thank you Lord for opening my eyes today to know the advantages of my lonely moments. Help me to pay attention to you when I â€™m alone to receive unusual idea from you, ideas that will turn the story of my family you will release to me today, connect me to heavenâ€™s antenna so I can receive heavenly informations in Jesus name! \r\n(lonely moment can be moment of divine profound ideas, maximise such times)\r\nOther text: Mark 6:45-47 for your reading.\r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 17:54:41'),(8,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-08',' Our Focus: WISDOM FOR RECONCILIATION ','DAY: SUN 8th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 32:3-20 \"...And say ye moreover, behold, thy servant Jacob is behind us, for he said I will appease him with the present that goeth before me, and afterwards I will see his face; peradventure he will accept of me\" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: WISDOM FOR RECONCILIATION \r\n\r\nSometime in life we may have to reconcile with some people we once fought with. As we grow in success and realize the need for peace with such people it will be wise to take the steps to make the peace happen just as Jacob did. We can go to such people or send gift of peace to secure such friendship back. But be sure such friendship will not jeopardize, you again. Reconciliation is good especially, in case where you are the one guilty. It is good to seek the forgiveness of the person you offend. You approach the person and tender apology for your wrong doing and God will grant you favour before the person. Secure reconciliation in other to prevent the devil from obstructing your journey to GREAT SUCCESS! May the Lord give you the grace. \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, help me touch this individual as I seek peace. Go ahead of me with your favour and let the person forgive me as I seek reconciliation, give me the right words to say in other to secure his/her forgiveness, help me to also forgive those who have offended me and create in me in clean heart from this moment on,  thank you for hearing me in Jesus name I pray. (Amen) \r\n(Taking step of reconciliation is a product of contribution, maturity and humility in Godâ€™s context)\r\nOther text: Matt. 18: 15-1 9 for your reading \r\n','2018-05-19 17:55:23'),(9,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-09',' Our Focus: YOU WILL MEET AN ANGEL OF GOD ','DAY: MON 9th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 32:1 \"And Jacob went on his way, and the angel of God met him.\r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU WILL MEET AN ANGEL OF GOD \r\n\r\nAs you prepare to go out today the lord is sending his angels your way. They shall come with good news for you and strike out evil that have touched you. The lord will surely send someone with the answer to your questions today. Hope is coming your way today. Get ready to meet someone with the solution to your problems. It is a divine arrangement. You shall meet DIVINE HELPERS that will wipe away your tears. Are you ready, for an encounter that will change your sorrow to joy today? \r\nThen sing this song as you pray: Pass me not oh gentle savior, hear my humble cry, while on others thou art calling, do not pass me by, Saviour 3x hear my humble cry... \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, as I step out today, let me meet the angels you have sent my way. My angels will locate me and I will locate them today, let me discern them by your spirit so I donâ€™t chase them away, Let there be special help for me today that will confirm your favour to me this day in Jesus name. \r\n(Angels are helpers  of your destiny they provide divine assistance to your vision)\r\nOther text: PS. 122:1 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 17:56:45'),(10,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-10','Our Focus: LONGING STRONGLY FOR YOUR \' FATHER\'S HOUSE \' ','DAY: TUES 10th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 31:30 \"And now, through thou wouldest needs be gone, because thou sore longest after thy fathers house...\" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: LONGING STRONGLY FOR YOUR \' FATHER\'S HOUSE \' \r\n\r\nEvery good child should always desire to see his father. Son to fatherâ€˜s relationship is very powerful. There is strong desire to see each except where the relationship is defaulted. Jacob longed for his fatherâ€™s house that he fled from Laban\'s house. How do you long for your fatherâ€™s house? If you are a true lover of God i.e, your heavenly father) you strongly desire to be in his house. Your passion for God\'s house reveals how much you love Him. You canâ€™t be comfortable anywhere when you ought to, be in His house. True lovers of God are never comfortable \' being in the work place when they suppose to be in the house of God. One of the ways you know how much you love God is your hunger for his house. Never you play with your passion for God\'s house it\'s a sign you are still in love with God. May you never lose your love for his house. \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Daddy, keep my heart on fire, let my zeal for your house never die. Help me to prefer your house to any other place in life, let my heart never be weary to go to your house, my love for you will not slack so the devil will not take advantage of it to destroy me (Amen). \r\n\r\nOther text: Ps. 122:1 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-19 17:58:02'),(11,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-11','Our Focus: YOU ARE COMING OUT OF SLAVERY ','DAY: WED 11th April., 2018 \r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 31:17-18 \"Then Jacob rose up, and set his son\'s, and his wives upon camels and all his goods which he had gotten in Pandanaram for to go and see Isaac his father unto the land of Canaan. \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU ARE COMING OUT OF SLAVERY \r\n\r\nToday, the Lord will take you out of slavery! Whatever has held you for so long in a condition you are not too satisfied with, the duration of that situation is over. You are getting out of it today in the name of Jesus. There is time for everything, and once the time of a season is over you are no more comfortable, the next should be your exist. Whatever situation you are no more comfortable with today, I command both you and your household to come out of it in the powerful name of Jesus Christ. No force can keep you back anymore, today is your day of JUBILEE receive your freedom, you are no more a slave to those circumstances, you are free, move out of them! \r\n\r\nOur Prayer Father, Take me out of SLAVERY, whatever I have been a slave to, set me free from it today, I declare I am no longer a slave to the devil, thank you for setting me free today from the house of bondage. I appreciate the release you are giving me to enter a new level today,  I will not disappoint you Lord in this level (Amen). \r\n(Those who stay brave will never end as slave in life)\r\nOther text: Ps. 17:13 for your reading \r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 17:58:52'),(12,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-12','Our Focus: THE POWER OF VOW ','DAY: THURS 12th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 31: 13 â€œI course God of bethel, where thou anointed the pillar; and where thou vowest a vow unto me now arise, get than out from this land, and return unto the land of thy kindred. \"\r\n\r\nOur Focus: THE POWER OF VOW \r\n\r\nl repeat this scripture today because of another vital lesson we need to learn in it. Why was God so interested in Jacob\'s success? Why did God shield Jacob from any hurt? And why did God enforce Jacob to return to his original inheritance? The answer to these is simply what I called THE POWER OF VOW. God\'s interest in Jacob\'s success was rooted in the vow that Jacob vowed to God in Gen. 28:20-22. Vow commits God exceptionally to your affair. He ensures your success and protection from external aggression. God also ensures you are back to your original favour if there is vow between you and him. If you find it difficult to succeed at anything you do, just try to make vow to God and see what will happen. Tell God, father if you do this for me I will honor you with this or that\" and watch what will happen, vow is a powerful key to unlock \r\nGod\'s favour. Try it today and seeâ€˜how God will commit himself to your course\r\n(vow has an enchanting force to provoke divine intervention in your unpleasant Circumstance)\r\nOur Prayer: Lord, as I vow to you today let my frustration come to an end over this issue. Let me keep to my vow so I donâ€™t incur curse, Now go ahead and make a vow to the lord over any issue that bothers you. You will witness his unusual favour. Honour your vow. \r\n\r\nOther text: Det. 23:21 for your reading\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 18:00:32'),(13,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-13','Our Focus: RETURNING TO YOUR IN HERITANCE ','DAY: FRI 13th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 31:13 \"I am the God of Bethel where thou anointed the pillar, and where thou vowed a vow unto me; now arise, get thee out from this land, and return unto the land of thy kindred.\" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: RETURNING TO YOUR IN HERITANCE \r\n\r\nCircumstances sent Jacob out of his father\'s house, but at the appointed time the Lord appeared and asked him to return to his land. Today is your appointed time to also return to your inheritance you have left due to certain circumstances. Have you been suffering out of your inheritance? Have you been sent out of your property? Have you been thrown out of what originally belongs to you? The Lord is saying return to your inheritance, go back and take your possession, the Lord has handled all those that made you leave earlier. Get back to your inheritance and no man will take it away from you anymore. Today you are returning to the favour(s) you have lost in time past, give him the glory for that! \r\n(Godâ€™s desire is not for you to lose your vital blessings forever. He steps in at the set time to return you to His original intent)\r\nOur Prayer: Father. take me back to my land that I was driven out from. Give me back all my possession that have been taken from me in hundred fold, all those who thought theyâ€™ve succeeded in sending me out will see me back on a higher level and theyâ€™ll be forced to bow to me, Take me back to my position I was demoted from and you shall be my God foreverâ€™ I see you going back to your inheritance today. \r\n\r\nOther text: Ps.126:1 -6 for your reading. \r\n\r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 18:02:18'),(14,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-14','Our Focus: YOUR DREAMS SHALL BE GOOD ONES ','DAY: SAT 14th April., 2018 \r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 31.10-12 \"A nd it came to pass at the time that the cattle conceived, that I lifted up my eyes, and saw in a dream, and behold, the rams which leaped upon the cattle were rings-treaked, speckled, and grisled. \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOUR DREAMS SHALL BE GOOD ONES \r\n\r\nWhat kind of dream do you dream? Jacob lifted up his eyes in a dream and saw how his flocks make progress. May you have progressive dreams, may you never dream terrible dreams. Anytime you dream terrible dreams cancel it with the blood of Jesus. Bad dreams are indication the devil is looming around you to do havoc. So you have a duty to resist such dreams instantly and ask for good dreams. Don\'t accept any negative dream you had, reject it and it will never prevail in your life. God loves you, therefore you need to have good and progressive dreams from him. Any dream where you see evil happening to you, it\'s not from God, I cancel its effect upon your life in Jesus name. Your dreams shall be good ones from now hence forth.\r\n(Good dreams are product of good walk with God)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, I disconnect myself from any evil dream, I cancel its effect upon my life, I am your child the devil has no right to threaten me in my dreams.  I will have Progressive dreams and not satanic dreams. Let my eyes see good things from now henceforth. in Jesus Christ name I pray (Amen) \r\n\r\nOther text: Gen. 37:5 -11 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 18:03:01'),(15,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-15','Our Focus: DIVINE FAVOUR TRANSFER ','DAY: SUN 15th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 31 :9 \"Thus God hath taken away the cattle of your father and given them to me â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: DIVINE FAVOUR TRANSFER \r\n\r\nWhen God\'s love is on you, he takes away some favour from some pe0ple and transfer it to you. I remember some time ago I gave somebody a gift and God told me to withdraw the gift and transfer it to another person (who really appreciated it so much). When you are ungrateful, God withdraws his favour from your life and transfer it to brethren that will value and thank him greatly for it. There are people that mishandle his favour, the Lord will take away those favour from them and transfer it to you, can I hear your Amen to that. Anyone that abuses or underrate God\'s favour will surely loose that favour to someone. When Saul abused the favour, he lost his throne to David, some people that are ahead of you in that office will soon lose their position to you. My God is embarking on favour transfer today. Everyone that has abused the divine privileges given to them shall lose it to you today in the wonderful name of Jesus. \r\n(when you obtain Godâ€™s favour, He can exchange other people other people favour for you especially those who disobey him)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, transfer your favour to me from everyone that has abused it. I will not possess the spirit of ingratitude that will make me lose my favour to someone else, As you transfer it to me let me never abuse but appreciate it so I can enjoy more from you. Let it be oh God in Jesus name I pray. \r\n\r\nOther text: 1 Sam 2:7-8 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-19 18:05:14'),(16,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-15','Our Focus: DIVINE FAVOUR TRANSFER ','DAY: SUN 15th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 31 :9 \"Thus God hath taken away the cattle of your father and given them to me â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: DIVINE FAVOUR TRANSFER \r\n\r\nWhen God\'s love is on you, he takes away some favour from some pe0ple and transfer it to you. I remember some time ago I gave somebody a gift and God told me to withdraw the gift and transfer it to another person (who really appreciated it so much). When you are ungrateful, God withdraws his favour from your life and transfer it to brethren that will value and thank him greatly for it. There are people that mishandle his favour, the Lord will take away those favour from them and transfer it to you, can I hear your Amen to that. Anyone that abuses or underrate God\'s favour will surely loose that favour to someone. When Saul abused the favour, he lost his throne to David, some people that are ahead of you in that office will soon lose their position to you. My God is embarking on favour transfer today. Everyone that has abused the divine privileges given to them shall lose it to you today in the wonderful name of Jesus. \r\n(when you obtain Godâ€™s favour, He can exchange other people other people favour for you especially those who disobey him)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, transfer your favour to me from everyone that has abused it. I will not possess the spirit of ingratitude that will make me lose my favour to someone else, As you transfer it to me let me never abuse but appreciate it so I can enjoy more from you. Let it be oh God in Jesus name I pray. \r\n\r\nOther text: 1 Sam 2:7-8 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-19 18:05:15'),(17,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-16',' Our Focus: GOD WILL RESIST ANYONE THAT WANTS TO HURT YOU. ','DAY: MON 16th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 6: 7 \"And ye know that with all my power I have some your father. And your father hath deceived me and changed my wages ten times; but God suffered him not hurt me.â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL RESIST ANYONE THAT WANTS TO HURT YOU. \r\n\r\nOne day, I saw a boy bigger than my son, he attempted to beat my son so I intervened and stopped him with a warning if he dare touch my son I will beat him mercilessly. I didn\'t care to ask who was guilty all I did was to resist his attempt to beat my son because he felt he was stronger than my son. So he left . frustrated and defeated when I stepped in, this is what the Lord will do for you, anyone that thought he/she is stronger than you and want to cheat you, my God will intervene speedily and resist such attempt to cheat you. If they are stronger than you they are not stronger than your father (i.e your God) He will deal with them mercilessly. God will resist any attempt to hurt you. You are SPECIAL TO HIM thank him for that. \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Thank you daddy, for resisting all those that wanted to cheat me because they felt they are stronger than me. Fight all those that are stronger than me and put them to shame. I will always rely on your strength and might and not mine alone, give me grace to glorify you through all in Jesus name (Amen). \r\n(if your ways pleases God, He resist anyone who tries to resist you)\r\nOur text: Isa. 41:1 0-1 4 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 18:07:12'),(18,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-17','Our Focus: GREATNESS ATTRACTs ENVY ','DAY: TUES 17th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 31:2 \"And Jacob beheld the countenance of Laban, and, behold, it was not toward him as before â€. \r\n\r\nOur Focus: GREATNESS ATTRACTs ENVY \r\n\r\nThere are people that will still be comfortable with you when you are still small, but, as soon as your greatness emerges their countenance will change towards you. There are some of your friends today that will turn away tomorrow when God will bless you richly. They are only friends because you are still poor as soon as God\'s favour shows up on you they will withdraw because they can\'t bear with your success. Greatness always attracts envy, once you start succeeding those who are not, are likely to start criticizing and turning away from you. Be ready for that as you succeed. Don\'t be moved, success is the factor of your excitement don\'t drop it because someone envies you. You will be great!_ \r\n(if you are not ready for envy then donâ€™t desire greatness. The greater you become, the more you will be envied)\r\nOur Prayer: Daddy, let me never be afraid of envy as it announces my greatness. Let your favour show on my life so I can discern who my true friends and enemies are, protect me from all envious people around me and help me never to be envious of anyoneâ€™s progress in Jesus name (Amen). \r\n\r\nOther text: Eccl. 4:4 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 18:08:20'),(19,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-18',' Our-Focus: NEVER MIND PEOPLE\'S GOSSIP ABOUT YOUR GREATNESS ','DAY: WED 18th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen 31:1 \"And he heard the words Laban\'s saying, Jacob hath taken away all that was our fathers and of that which was our fathers hath he gotten all this \r\n\r\nOur-Focus: NEVER MIND PEOPLE\'S GOSSIP ABOUT YOUR GREATNESS \r\n\r\nBeware, if you are making progress in life. People will gossip about you out of envy they will speak malicious words just to frustrate you. Never respond to them if they are making progress they won\'t gossip about you. People who make progress don\'t have time to gossip about others because they are so busy doing their work. People who gossip about other people\'s success are usually failures. So don\'t bother yourself with them you just keep moving, don\'t relent they will be totally locked up in shame one day. Gossipers are going nowhere so don\'t let them distract you. Keep succeeding while they keep gossiping, they will be your slaves soon! People talk about you because you are GREAT. Nobody waste his time on a NOBODY you are SOMEBODY (SPECIAL) so they must gossip about you! \r\n(if people gossip about you, be sure you are on the right course. Gossip is part of ministries of those who have failed in life)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, help me never to relent even as my ears hear gossip of what people say about my progress. Distractions will not sway my focus in another direction, help to maintain my path to greatness at all times, Help me to keep doing my work well so I will not end with the mendicants of life... (Amen). \r\n\r\nOther text: Neh. 6 :8-9 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 23:45:30'),(20,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-19','Our Focus: YOU SHALL BE STRONGER THAN YOUR COMPETITORS','DAY: THURS 19th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 30 42 \"But when the cattle were feeble, he put them not in so the feeble ones were Laban\' S, and the stronger Jacob\' sâ€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU SHALL BE STRONGER THAN YOUR COMPETITORS \r\n\r\nGod gave Jacob an unusual wisdom that made him possess stronger flocks than Laban\'s. An idea can make you stronger than your competitors, I pray for you today, God will bless you with unusual wisdom that will make you possess greater favour than your competitors. You will secure a unique grace to do things better than your colleagues and you will be stronger and richer in favour in the name Of Jesus Christ. It takes just an idea to mark your difference from others doing that same business you are in. my God will mark you out and you will outweigh them in favour!\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, bless me with an unusual business idea that will make me stronger than all my competitors, I receive that unique style, skill, mode of doing things so I can be preferred above my competitors in Jesus name I pray \r\n(Amen). \r\n(Godâ€™s wisdom injects with the ability to outweigh your competitors)\r\nOther text: Pr. 4:7-9 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 23:46:39'),(21,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-20',' Our Focus: YOUR GREATNESS IS NOT LIMITED TO AN AXIS ','DAY: FRI 20th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 28: 14 \"...and thou shall spread abroad to the west, and to the east, and to the north and to the south; and m thee and in thy seed shall all the families of the earth be blessed. \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOUR GREATNESS IS NOT LIMITED TO AN AXIS \r\n\r\nReal greatness is beyond an axis, it goes to all the four axis of the earth, the west, the east, the north and the south. You may start affecting an axis but that is not the \r\nultimate. The Lord will make you spread to all the axis of the earth as days and year roll by. \r\n\r\nGet ready to affect more than your immediate environment. You shall be a blessing to all and not to few people. You may begin by blessing few but with time the Lord will expand your sphere of influence to many. You are sent to all nations and that is where you are heading to. You are not limited. in your greatness. You shall spread to all cardinal axis of the earth, Don\'t relent in your commitment, keep working hard, one day from that your little place you will be raised to touch the whole world, it will happen for you in Jesus name!.\r\n\r\nOur prayer: Father, I appreciate your great plan for me to, be a blessing to all nations, though my beginning is small but I know one day you will cause me to feed many nations of the earth so shall it be in Jesus Christ name. \r\n(Divine Greatness progresses to all axis of the world. You may start in an axis but will spread to others with times)\r\nOther text: Luke 12:32 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-19 23:47:24'),(22,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-21',' Our Focus: GOD WILL USE YOU TO INCREASE SOMEONE','DAY: SAT 21st April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 30:30 â€œFor it was little which thou hadst before I came, and it is now increased unto a multitude; and the lord hath blessed thee since my coming! \r\n\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL USE YOU TO INCREASE SOMEONE\r\n\r\nYou shall be an agent of increase and not decrease to someone. As you go out today, God will use you to increase someone. God will pass his grace through you to remove the disgrace in someone\'s life. Somebody will come your way today sent by God, don\'t despise the person, Let God use you for that person. You will increase the joy of that person and in return the Lord will increase you. Be ready to be used today to help someone increase and your life will never decreaseâ€™ in Jesus name. \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Use me today as you have said to increase someone today so I can reap your favour also, I will not be used by the devil to pull someone down so I wonâ€™t also be pulled down by other people,  as I move someone forward, Lord move me forward also in Jesus Christ name I pray. \r\n(Those who make others better are agent of change while those who make others worse are killers of destiny)\r\nOther text: Is. 60:15 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-19 23:48:41'),(23,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-22',' Our Focus: WHATEVER YOU WANT WILL BE GIVEN TO YOU ','DAY: SUN 22nd April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 30:28 â€œAnd Laban said unto Jacob Appoint me thy wages and I will pay them. \r\n\r\nOur Focus: WHATEVER YOU WANT WILL BE GIVEN TO YOU \r\n\r\nToday is a special day for you, you have an open check before on this morning. Your master is saying ask whatever you want me to give you and I will give you. God has seen your service to him, how faithfully and loving you have been to him. And this day he is rising up With this favour for you ask whatever you want me to give you and I will. Just go ahead right now on your knees and tell him what you want him to do for you this day and this week, behold you shall see it done in Jesus name.\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Just tell him whatever you personally desire for your life and family you Will surely receive the grant from him right away go ahead andâ€˜ pray. \r\n(when you have an opportunity to ask for things, seek potentials instead of material. Ask for ideas and not money Ideas are machines that make money)\r\nOther text: Ps.20:1-9 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-19 23:49:36'),(24,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-23','INDISPENSABLE  Our Focus: YOU SHALL BE ','DAY: MON 23rd April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 30:27 \"And Laban said unto him (Jacob) I \' pray thee, if I have found favour in thine eyes, tarry, for I have learnt by experience that the lord hath blessed me for thy sake. \" \r\nINDISPENSABLE \r\nOur Focus: YOU SHALL BE \r\n\r\nEveryone of us knows what SALT is to our meal. It has such an â€˜ indispensable value to flavor our meal. Lack of salt in your delicacies will make it tasteless. Salt is indispensable; God is putting such a value on your life wherever you find yourself, your superior, neighbors, friends and family will never want you to leave them. It is a blessing for people to desire you stay longer with them. It is a sign you mean so much to them. If you mean nothing noâ€˜ one bothers with your departure. But when you are a favour people want you to always be with them. I declare in the name of the lord you shall be a favour people will never want to lose. May you carry such a value that will make a great blessing to your host and they will never want to lose you in Jesus name. You are indispensable! \r\n(if your life is viable, you will be indispensable. If you are a liability you are treated as nonentity)\r\nOur Prayer: Lord Jesus, give me what it takes to be highly valued by everyone around me, let me be a SALT and not a SORE to my society, make me a GRACE and not a DISGRACE to my host thank you Lord for answering me in Jesus name I pray. \r\n\r\nOther text: Is. 60:1 5 for your reading. \r\n\r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:01:50'),(25,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-24',' Our Focus: YOUR REPROACH SHALL BE TAKEN AWAY','DAY: TUES 24th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text. Gen. 30. 23 \"And God remembered Rachael and God harkened unto her, and opened her womb. And she conceived and bares a son and said, God hath taken away my reproach. \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOUR REPROACH SHALL BE TAKEN AWAY \r\n\r\nReproach is anything that makes you feel sad, inadequate, shameful and insufficient. It could be lack of husband, child, job, money etc whatever makes you feel uncomfortable is a reproach. Today I pray it out of your life in the name of Jesus Christ. There was a time I found it very difficult to feed my family, I could not provide enough for the house. The experience was too shameful for me but God took that reproach away in my life someday, after intensive calling on God for his help, the Lord heard me and took that painful experience away in my life and now I can joyfully provide for my house. This will happen to you, whatever you are going through that should not be, the Lord shall change the circumstance for good. The reproach is taken away today and his favour will now approach you. \r\n(whatever irritates people away from you is a reproach)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, take away today in my life everything that makes me feel ashamed and inadequate, all those things people mock me for let it be erased from my life today, provide me a blessing that will turn my reproach to approach, I will celebrate today in Jesus Christ name I pray! \r\n\r\nOther text: Ps. 123 :1 -4 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:02:49'),(26,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-25','Our Focus: GOD WILL HARKEN TO YOU ','DAY: WED 25th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 30:17 â€œAnd God harkened unto Leah, and she conceived, and bare Jacob the fifth son \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL HARKEN TO YOU \r\n\r\nWhatever you earnestly desire from the Lord, he will hear you and do it for you. The Lord will answer. The result of your agonizing prayer is about to come. He can\'t ignore your call, he will attend to you. You are special to him and therefore your answer is sure. Get ready to receive the answer to your prayers as you go out today you will see his grace at work. As he harkened to Leah he will answer you today in Jesus Christ name. \r\n(Godâ€™s ears are open to the helpless who cries to Him in  truth and in spirit)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, harken to my long time cry and give that which my soul long for, ask him whatever you need from him, tell him your desires and he will respond to you. I shall see your favour today, thank you Lord in Jesus name I pray (Amen).\r\n\r\nOther text: Ps. 3 4 :5-6 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:03:56'),(27,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-26','Our Focus: MAY YOU NOT BE A BEGGAR ','DAY: THURS 26th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 30: 14-15 \"Then Rachael said to Leah, give me I pray thee of thy son\'s mandrake. And she said unto her, ts it a small matter that thou hast taken my husband? And would thou take away my son \'s mandrakes also?...\"\r\n\r\nOur Focus: MAY YOU NOT BE A BEGGAR \r\n\r\nI have discovered, one of the ways you can ever hear the most repulsive statement of your life, is for you to be a beggar. When you beg, you give people the right to insult you and also to look down on you. Begging looks like a free gift you receive from people, but the reproach it carries could be very unappealing When you beg ,people use the opportunity to pour their grieves on you. And you have no choice than to listen since you begged them for something. Begging will make you lose your significance before the people. Begging keeps you at the mercy of people. It makes you a slave to the giver and crushes your sense of dignity. Once you are a beggar then you have no choice than to bear whatever insult people have to offer you. A beggar indeed has no choice! May you never be a beggar my God will give you the ability to work and have what you need to enjoy your life. Let whatever people give you be the reward of service rendered to them, thus, you will not be bound to men\'s reproach. You will not be a beggar anymore! \r\n(there is no certificate of honour for any beggar in life. donâ€™t settle for begging so you donâ€™t ruin your honour in life)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, give me your wisdom to work and earn my Living, let me never be a beggar at the mercy of people. Let whatever people give to me be a reward of the service I rendered to them, thank you Lord in Jesus name I pray! \r\n\r\nOther text: Pro. 22: 7 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:04:34'),(28,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-27',' Our Focus: YOU SHALL FIND FAVOUR ','\r\nDAY: FRI 27th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 30:14 â€œAnd Reuben went in the days of wheat harvest, and found mandrakes in the field, and brought them unto his mother Leah. \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU SHALL FIND FAVOUR \r\n\r\nYour going out today shall be to favour. You shall reap a favour in your place of work today. You shall come back home with mandrakes in your hands. You shall not return home empty handed. Your hands shall be filled with his great favour. Please Open your hands to God this morning and prophesy that, you shall reap in abundance today God\'s favour. Something good must come to your hands today. I speak favour to your hands. as you go. You must come back home with evidence. Share your testimony with us on the favour you encounter today. It is well with you! \r\n(favour is extra provision to compliment your labour, you need it to boost your labour at regular interval)\r\nOur Prayer: Thank you father for your favour on me today my hands shall be filled with miraculous provision. I shall return with mandrakes in my hand today in Jesus Mighty name (A men). \r\n\r\nOther text: Ps.126:6 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:05:35'),(29,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-28',' Our Focus: BEWARE OF PROVOCATION ','DAY: SAT 28th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen.30: 2 \"And Jacob \'s anger was kindled against Rachel; and he said, am I in God\'s stead, who hath withheld from thee the fruit of the womb ? \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: BEWARE OF PROVOCATION \r\n\r\nI could hear in my spirit, someone will provoke you today, but don\'t over react. It\'s a set up from Hell to distort your day, but those devils have failed as the Lord has hinted you. Don\'t be angry just smile at every slightest attempt to flare you. Don\'t be provoked no matter what may come your way today. Thank him for everything you may have to sing songs like \"I give you thank, I give praise for I know that all things work together for our good, I give you thanks, I give you praise for by faith I know your grace will see me through.\" Oh yes his grace will surely see you through as you overcome the provocation, there shall be a presentation from above to you. Don\'t be disturbed, cheer up something great is on the way for you in Jesus Christ name, you will have it soon. Let no man provoke you to speak unwisely! \r\n(soft answer turns away wrath. Guide your utterance and prevent evil occurance)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, give me victory over every attempt to distort and provoke me today. I cancel every plan of the devil to frustrate my joy today by the authority in Jesus name (Amen). \r\n\r\nOther text: Pr. 27:3 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:06:22'),(30,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-29','Our Focus: NEVER ENVY ANYONE ','DAY: SUN 29th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 30:1 â€œAnd when Rachel saw that she bare Jacob no children, Rachael envied her sister; and said unto Jacob, give me children, or else I die. â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: NEVER ENVY ANYONE \r\n\r\nEnvy is to have a bad, mad and sad feeling over other people\'s achievement(s). Having an unhappy mood over your neighbour\'s achievement. It is a bad spirit that will never allow you progress. Once you are not happy with someone\'s progress, you will never progress in that direction. Envy will make you sick whenever you see the person you envy, your health is distorted, Envy torments its host. it makes you restless, helpless and reckless. An envious person can kill even his blood brother or sister. Envy is a terrible spirit never, ever â€œallow it in your life. \r\n\r\nThe way to deal with envy is to always appreciate the progress of others knowing well this will help you to progress also. When you rejoice with other people\'s progress, you can\'t lack progress. Whatever anybody has, convince yourself, with time and by the grace of God, I will have mine, in this way you will deal with envy in your life. If you permit envy it will destroy your joyâ€˜ and make you miserable, so don\'t allow its grip on you. Be focus and confident the lord will bless you likewise in HIS TIME! I see you free from envy this day in Jesus name. \r\n(Envy blocks your greatness. It also bring rottenness to your bones, avoid it)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, break the yoke of envy in my life, let it never sit in my heart. Free me from its horrible grip, so I can rejoice with everyone succeeding around me as my success comes. \r\nOther text: Job 5:2 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:07:11'),(31,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-04-30',' Our Focus: THE LORD WILL DO SOMETHING FOR YOU THAT WILL PROVOKE HIS PRAISE ','DAY: MON 30th April., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 29:35 \"And she conceived again, and bare a son and, she said, Now will I praise the lord therefore she called his name Judah; and left bearing. \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: THE LORD WILL DO SOMETHING FOR YOU THAT WILL PROVOKE HIS PRAISE \r\n\r\nIn this new month, the Almighty will give you something great that will provoke his praise from your heart. What others lack God will give you sacks of such blessings. This month, be sure to receive a favour that will stir his praise in your life. Wonderful things will happen for you, you shall actualize some vision you\'ve conceived all the while. This season you will experience the birth of achievements that will compel his praise in your mouth. It sounds in my spirit again and again \"I WILL DO SOMETHING FOR YOU THAT WILL PROVOKE MY PRAISE IN YOUR LIFE\" oh Halleluyah! Do you believe these words? Then be ready for God out pouring of favour. Your hands shall, receive unusual favour from the Lord. Every day of this year you will have reason to praise him! So shall it be for you (Amen). \r\n(when God perform miracles in your life. You will expressly become a composer before Him)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, thank you for what you will do for me this month, you have promised to bless me \' with a favour that will provoke your praise on my lips. Lord I believe and desperately await your wonderful favour as I will praise you with all my heart. \r\n\r\nOther text: Luke 1:57-58 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:08:07'),(32,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-01',' Our Focus: YOU SHALL GIVE BIRTH TO YOUR MIRACLE','\r\nDAY: TUES 1st MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 29:32 \"And Leah conceived, and bare a son; and son; and she called his name Reuben, for she said, surely the Lord hath looked upon my affliction; now therefore my husband will love me. \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU SHALL GIVE BIRTH TO YOUR MIRACLE \r\n\r\nAs Leah conceived and gave birth successfully so I pray for you this day, whatever pregnancy you are carrying you will give birth to it successfully. Is there anything you conceive to achieve? You shall have it in Jesus name. Whatever you are thinking of having could it be a house? A car, a job, an admission or a baby? Whatever it is that you are heavily pregnant of, receive grace to have it in Jesus name. You will . rejoice as the Lord has looked upon your affliction. Your desired miracles shall be born and God will be glorified. Whatever you have conceived of, receive the grace to give birth today by his grace! \r\n(when grace is at work in your life miracles are born on a consistent basis)\r\nOur Prayer: Thank you Lord because you will help me to give birth to the dream in my womb. I will give birth to something great that the world will recognize me for.  I count on your grace to enable me achieve all I have conceived.\r\n\r\nOther text: Isa 66: 7 for your reading\r\n','2018-05-20 00:09:02'),(33,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-02','Our Focus: GOD WILL HELP THE HATED','DAY: WED 2nd MAY, 2018 \r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 29:31 \"And when the lord saw that Leah was hated, he opened her womb; but Rachael was barren \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL HELP THE HATED \r\n\r\nIf you are hated for doing nothing wrong, God will step in and help you. God specializes in helping those who are hated for right course. If the hatred people have for you is envy motivated, don\'t worry God is strongly by your side. The more they hate you the higher God will lift you so they can be ashamed. God saw that Leah was hated, so he opened her womb. Those who hate you for no wrong causes will soon realize you are making more progress. \r\n\r\nNever let the hatred of men weigh you down hold unto God\'s help. He will never leave you to the mercy of your haters. God , will open your womb of success for more conception to torment those who hate you! Don\'t be moved keep on your good work your haters will soon be ashamed! \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, stand for my help let my haters be ashamed cause me to progress more in spite of how I am being hated for your sake. Let those who hate me regret their action as you favour me today in Jesus name. \r\n\r\nOther text PS. 2:1 -1 2 for your reading.\r\n','2018-05-20 00:10:06'),(34,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-03',' Our Focus: YOU SHALL FIND WHATEVER YOU ARE LOOKING FOR ','DAY: THURS 3rd MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 29:4-6 . \"And Jacob said unto them ... know Laban the son of Nahor? And they said, we know him and he said unto them is he well? And they said He is well... \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU SHALL FIND WHATEVER YOU ARE LOOKING FOR \r\n\r\nJacob found people who know the exact person he wanted to see, Laban the son of Nahor. He was so excited to meet people that knew who he was looking for. Hear what the spirit is saying, are you searching for someone or something, today by the grace Of God, you will find who/what you are looking for. Today is a day to find what your heart earnestly desires. Get set to see the person/thing you are looking for. I Open your eyes, I speak to your feet today, right direction to where that thing is and you will find it in Jesus name! Whatever you are searching for today you will find it give him thanks in advance!\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, let me see the person my soul has been searching for. That thing I \'ve really been looking for cause me to see it today according to your word for me today thank you dear Lord. \r\n\r\nOther text: Luke I 5 :32 for your reading \r\n','2018-05-20 00:10:39'),(35,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-04','Our Focus: EVERY STONE ON YOUR WELL\'S MOUTH SHALL BE ROLLED AWAY','DAY: FRI 4th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 29:2b-3 â€œ... and a great stone was upon the well\'s mouth, and thither were all the flocks gathered: and they rolled the stone from the well \'s mouth, and watered the sheep... \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: EVERY STONE ON YOUR WELL\'S MOUTH SHALL BE ROLLED AWAY \r\n\r\nJust as the great stone on the well\'s mouth was rolled away so the Hooks are watered. So I command as you go out today, every barrier on your route rolled away in Jesus name. Whatever stands as stumbling block \' to your favour (promotion) I roll them away by death, sickness or dismissal. Whoever will not allow you to secure the comfort the lord has for you shall be rolled away. Shout EVERY STONE (PERSON OR GROUP OF PERSONS) BLOCKING MY PROGRESS I ROLL YOU AWAY TODAY BY THE AUTHORITY IN THE MIGHTY NAME OF Jesus Christ! You can no longer stand in the way of my success. I\'m going for my favour today and i have it in Jesus name the barriers are removed, you will have your victory. \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Say; Every stumbling block of the past become a stepping stone today to my favour: I am going in the name of the Lord so all hurdles be removed right now, my favour will get to me and no stone will hinder it in Jesus Christ name\r\n','2018-05-20 00:11:15'),(36,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-05','Our Focus: GOD WILL MAKE YOU OASIS ','DAY: SAT 5th MAY., 2018 \r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 29:1-2 â€œ... And he looked, and behold a well in the field, and lo there were three flocks of sheep lying by it; for out of that well they watered the flocks \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL MAKE YOU OASIS \r\n\r\nAn oasis is a place of hope in the midst of hopelessness. It\'s just like finding a well in the desert. It becomes a place for everyone to rush and get water so they can be refreshed. God will raise you as an oasis for your family. Perhaps no one has risen before to any reasonable height, the Lord will raise you in his favour that you will bring hope to your family. In the midst of hardship, God will use you to bring surplus. All those who are hopeless around you will soon find happiness through you. You shall be a well for your household in their desert experience. God will use you to put an end to record of hardship in your generation. God will use the Refiner\'s House as OASIS IN THE DESERT to put an end to the suffering of people in this land and beyond we shall be like a well in the field in Jesus mighty name. \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, lift me to a reasonable height today, make a channel of hope to all the hopeless around me, use me to bring comfort to where people are frustrated and disappointed. Let me be an oasis in the desert of our generation and use me to put an end to suffering and hardship in the lives of those around me and this generation, Amen.\r\n\r\nOther text: Isa. 35 :1 -2 for your reading. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:12:40'),(37,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-06',' Our Focus: THE ADVANTAGE OF PAYING YOUR TITHE','DAY: SUN 6th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 28:22 â€œAnd this stone, which I have set for a  pillar shall be God \'s house and of all that thou shall give me I will surely give the tenth unto thee \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: THE ADVANTAGE OF PAYING YOUR TITHE \r\n\r\nWhen you commit ten percent of all your earnings to God, He ensures your business does not fail. He also protects your family from evil attacks in form of death, fire disaster and accident. When you pay your tithe God fights anyone that intends to ruin your business. A man from Nasarawa State intended to ruin one of our brother\'s business (who pays his tithe to God regularly) what happened? That man died a  mysterious death because of his evil intention against a tither. God does not take it light with anyone who dares a tither. If you don\'t pay tithe, you incapacitate God from helping your work. No matter how you struggle and work hard if God is not reign in your work, you will never enjoy that work. I advise you today never to play with your tithe or God will never show up in your favour. May you be fruitful to him. \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, thank you for sensitizing me on the importance of tithing, help me to be faithful in my tithe and offering, let me not be responsible for the downfall of my business for lack of tithing, help me dear Lord in Jesus name I pray. (Amen). \r\n\r\nOther text: Mal. 3 :812 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:13:32'),(38,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-07',' Our Focus: RISING WITH A PLAN FOR GOD\'S KINGDOM ','DAY: MON 7th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOUR TEXT: Gen. 28:1 8~22 â€œAnd Jacob rose up early m the morning, and took the stone that he had put for his pillows, set it up for a pillar, and poured oil upon the top of it. And Jacob vowed a vow, this stone which I have set for a pillar shall be God\'s house. â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: RISING WITH A PLAN FOR GOD\'S KINGDOM \r\n\r\nJacob rose up early with a vow to do something for the house of the Lord as the Lord blesses him. Can I ask you a question beloved, when last did you support or propose a project for the house of God? When last did you do anything special for your church? Did you rise up one morning with a thought to buy a wall clock, or plastic seats or a glass pulpit for your church? You only wake up with plans for yourself, you never bother about the needs in the house of God, how can we be bless that way? I suggest, for you to greatly secure God\'s presence and favour, you must learn to do something for his house. Take a step today look in the church find out a need and provide it, then see how God will turn your work around. Just make up your mind-right now and provide a special gift for the house of God by Sunday morning and see how God in return will bless your work. May you have his kingdom in mind! \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, show me something to provide for your house so I can experience your favour in my life every day. Help me be a need to your house so you will attend to the needs in my life. Help me never to be satisfied seeing a need in your house and not providing it. Bless me so I never have an excuse not to sow in your house.\r\n\r\nOther text: PS.102:1 3-1 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:14:24'),(39,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-08','Our Focus: GOD WILL DELIVER YOU FROM THE POWER OF THE GRAVE','DAY: TUES 8th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOUR TEXT: Psa 49:15 â€œBut God will redeem my soul from the Power of the grave, for He shall receive meâ€\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL DELIVER YOU FROM THE POWER OF THE GRAVE\r\nI recently visited a country and a day was declared public holiday, then I asked what was the public holiday for? They told me its a grave decorating day. I saw people at the grave of their loved ones putting flowers on the grave. I was grieved in the spirit. Why? Most of those loved ones in these graves are young people who died in their prime of their lives.\r\nMost of those loved ones in the grave died of penury. Their dreams in life were cut short. It saddens me to see thousand of young vibrant unfulfilled destinies lie in the grave. This is not Godâ€™s plan at all! Sin is responsible for untimely death! The original plan of God is for us to live an advanced fulfilled life. God wants us to die in a good old age (Gne 25:8, Psa 91:14-16) however, desire for worldly things crushed the days of many to the grave. \r\nGreed for money in our society has resulted to production of fake drugs, robbery and prostitution, all these crushed the lives of many! Our environment is highly polluted this has negative impact in our health. In view of this, many are sent to early grave.\r\nI pray for you this morning, nothing will cut your days short! My God will protect you from all evil, you will fulfill your years and die in a good old age. You will not meet untimely death today! My God will deliver you from the power of grave.\r\n(Grace can shield you from untimely grave experience, you need his grace to escape the grave stronghold)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, thank you for the word of life, keep my family from lying in the grave untimely, let your grace defend me from every evil force seeking my destiny so I can fulfill my dreams on earth for you Lord. Thanks for hearing me in Jesus name I pray!\r\n\r\nOther text: PS.49:8-9 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:15:49'),(40,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-09','Our Focus: I AM WITH YOU ','DAY: WED 9th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOUR TEXT: Gen. 28: 15 â€œAnd, behold, I am with thee, and will keep them all places wither thou goest, and will bring thee again into this land, for I will not leave thee, until I have done that which I have spoken to thee of â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: I AM WITH YOU \r\n\r\nIf there is anything that ever gives me confidence is this statement \"I AM WITH YOU\" when the Lord assures you he is with you, then you are very safe. No evil can attack you and prevail. You can \'t go for an interview and fail. You can \'t travel and have accident, if accident occurs nothing will happen to you because He is with you! The greatest safety statement we can have is the above words I AM WITH YOU. This is the assurance the Lord is giving you today â€œI am with you\" so anything you do today shall be successful, no evil will touch you. Go out with great confidence He is with you all evil must bow before you, walk to your favour today.\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, continue to be with me so I can continue to enjoy your safety and favour in Jesus name. I will enjoy your favour, protection, provision at all times. Clear every evil in my way today, order my steps to good things today in Jesus name I pray.\r\n\r\nOther text: Matt. 28:20 for your  reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:16:30'),(41,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-10',' Our Focus: NEVER BE DISCOURAGED BECAUSE OTHERS EXCEL AROUND YOU','DAY: THURS 10th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOUR TEXT: Psa 49:16	 â€œDo not be afraid when one becomes rich when the glory of his house is increased for when he dies he shall carry nothing away; his glory shall not descend after himâ€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: NEVER BE DISCOURAGED BECAUSE OTHERS EXCEL AROUND YOU\r\nI want to encourage someone today, you woke up sad this morning. A thought is on your mind, why are others rising and nothing is working for me? Calm down, the Lord knows you, he recognizes your efforts, he will reward you at the due time, not all that glitters around you is REAL GOLD!\r\nWe live in the world of superficial luxuries. There are things people do that can kill your FAITHFULNESS to God. You have to be careful, not everyone you see flashy made it the right way. donâ€™t ask God why are you not blessing me like those people around me. Godâ€™s blessing is not in a rush, it comes gradually. Donâ€™t be sad, you are on the right course. Stay faithful at your duty post. God will reward you soon. Remember all these material is only temporal, none will go with you when you die according to our opening text. Donâ€™t let your heart be worried, you will make it in the right way, it may not come in a flashy manner but you will have peace of God and hope of eternal glory. Everything in this world end the day you die, your soul alone will return to give account. So donâ€™t give up your eternity for materialism. Your sincerity is a virtue with hope of eternity. Never allow worry. The Lord will minister to your needs one after the other. Thank him for possessing his fear and you will know very soon that it pays to fear him! Stay strong and be lifted as you go out today.\r\n(NOT ALL THAT GLITTERS IS REAL GOLD, NEVER LET THE SUCCESS OF OTHERS DEPRESS YOU, YOU CANT TELL HOW REAL THEY ARE)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, thank you for the word, give me grace to lean on you and never to be discouraged, help me to stand to the end and it shall be well with me. AMEN\r\nOther text: PS.4:13-19 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:17:34'),(42,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-11',' Our Focus: YOU NEED THE BLESSING OF UNDERSTANDING','\r\nDAY: FRI 11th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOUR TEXT: Psa 49:20	â€œA man who is in honour, yet does not understand is like the beasts that perishâ€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU NEED THE BLESSING OF UNDERSTANDING\r\n\r\nUnderstanding who you are in God is a great blessing! Ignorance of your divine status robs you of your power in God! 3 things you must understand about yourself. \r\n1. UNDERDTAND WHO YOU ARE: know your creation in Godâ€™s image so you are not an ordinary person. You are a peculiar person created for Godâ€™s purpose so you are a threat at all levels to the devil (1 Pet 2:8-9)\r\n2. UNDERSTAND WHERE YOU ARE GOING: you are on earth to do the will of God, so you donâ€™t live by what people say but what God says to you. Your passion might not be someoneâ€™s passion. You are very unique, know what gives you joy and satisfaction and focus on it!\r\n3. UNDERSTAND WHO CAN GO WITH YOU: your identity and purpose will determine those you relate with. In life a man of understanding does not relate comfortably with everybody but with those willing to appreciate your person and passion. Lion relate with lions, cat relates with cats. So you must understand those who can go with you in your journey of success otherwise you suffer frustration!\r\nI pray for you today you will walk with this blessing of understanding and change your course from failure to success. Have a wonderful day!\r\n(understanding yourself helps you understand who to relate with. Self identity helps right relationship. Mind yourself then mind who you relate with)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, I receive the blessing of understanding my identity to determine my purpose and relationships. As a lion, may I not keep myself in the midst of rats so I donâ€™t lose my tenacity and dignity! AMEN\r\nOther text: Prov. 13:20 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:18:38'),(43,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-12','Our Focus: YOUR GREATNESS IS NOT LIMITED TO AN AXIS ','DAY:  SAT 12th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 28: 14 \"...and thou shall spread abroad to the west, and to the east, and to the north and to the south; and m thee and in thy seed shall all the families of the earth be blessed. \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOUR GREATNESS IS NOT LIMITED TO AN AXIS \r\n\r\nReal greatness is beyond an axis, it goes to all the four axis of the earth, the west, the east, the north and the south. You may start affecting an axis but that is not the ultimate. The Lord will make you spread to all the axis of the earth as days and year roll by. Get ready to affect more than your immediate environment. You shall be a blessing to all and not to few people. You may begin by blessing few but with time the lord will expand your sphere of influence to many. You are sent to all nations and that is where you are heading to. You are not limited. in your greatness. You shall spread to all cardinal axis of the earth, Don\'t relent in your commitment, keep working hard, one day from that your little place you will be raised to touch the whole world, it will happen for you in Jesus name!.\r\n\r\nOur prayer: Father, I appreciate your great plan for me to be a blessing to all nations, though my beginning is small but I know one day you will cause me to feed many nations of the earth, broaden my circumference by the reason of your favour and wisdom on my life and let me affect lives positively for you, so shall it be in Jesus Christ name. \r\n\r\nOther text: Luke 12:32 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:19:50'),(44,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-13','Our Focus: THE MIGHTY ONE IS CALLING YOU OUT!','DAY:  SUN 13th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOUR TEXT: Psa 50:1	â€œThe mighty one, God the Lord has spoken and called the earth from the rising of the sun to its going downâ€\r\nOur Focus: THE MIGHTY ONE IS CALLING YOU OUT!\r\n\r\nI remember some year back when some of our children played on a carpet outside unknown to them, they were on top of a well! Someone alerted us of the disaster they were playing on so we came there and called them wisely to leave there, as soon as they yielded and left, the carpet fell into about 3o feet depth well, can you see that?!\r\nIf not that we called them out of that place imagine what could have happened to them! I decree this morning THE MIGHTY ONE, GOD THE LORD will call you out of any danger zone! Anywhere evil is about to fall on you, the Lord will call you out of that horizon! Any car you will board that will crash you today, God will call you out of it. This has happened to me before, God called me out of a car and the car later crashed with other passengers dead in it. God called me out!\r\nToday, any danger looming, the Lord will call you out of that place. You will not crash to evil as you proceed this day, I see God calling and sensitizing your spirit out of danger zone.\r\nOur Prayer: Father, call me out of any doom about to befall me, let your voice overwhelm my spirit so I donâ€™t crash to evil zone as I go this day, let your hand guide me safe so evil will not prevail on me in Jesus Name.\r\nOther text: PS.91:1 -10 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:20:47'),(45,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-14',' Our Focus: GOD WILL PERFECT YOUR LIFE WITH HIS GLORY','DAY: MON 14th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOUR TEXT: Psa 50:2	â€œout of Zion, the perfection of beauty, God will shine forthâ€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL PERFECT YOUR LIFE WITH HIS GLORY\r\n\r\nYou know every morning after taking your bath, you apply something like cosmetics to bring out your beauty before facing the day. Beauty requires combination of something to enhance. Today, the Lord will perfect your life with his glory. Whatever you need to make you glorious and attractive, My God will give you. Whatever will add glory to you get ready, my God will out it on you. It can be a spouse job, mobility, financial favour, salvation and other good things that will make you colourful. This is a day of the Lord PERFECTION OF BEAUTY so get set for his glory. Shout FATHER PERFECT MY LIFE TODAY WITH YOUR GLORY 3X so shall it be in Jesus name\r\n(Godâ€™s glory will perfect your life story)\r\nOur Prayer: Father, perfect the story of my life today with your glory, add to my life whatever I need to make me better than who I was, let your light shine on my so my story will come with great testimony today! Thank you Lord for answering my prayer in Jesus name!\r\nOther text: Isa 61:1-3 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:21:36'),(46,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-15','Our Focus: GOD WILL ARISE TO FIGHT FOR YOU','DAY: TUES 15th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Psa 50:3	â€œOur God shall come and shall  not keep silent; a fire shall devour before him and it shall be very tempestuousâ€\r\n\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL ARISE TO FIGHT FOR YOU\r\n\r\nHave you been molested and you felt like embarking on a suicide mission? Hold on, donâ€™t try that! The Lord sent me to tell you that he will fight for yoy. Those who took advantage of your innocence and simplicity will face the anger of God. The Lord is aware of all they did to you and he is rising up furiously to avenge your case!\r\ndonâ€™t kill yourself, stop crying, your helper is here to vindicate you, I trust him to help you fight this battle you cant fight it so donâ€™t harm yourself.. I see him crushing those who mocked and crushed you. Cheer up he is on your side and ready to pay back your molesters. The helper of the oppressed is here to take on the battle for you. Glorify him for stepping to your rescue his fire will judge the wicked afflicting the righteous, oh yes he is here for you!\r\n(God fights for those canâ€™t fight for themselves he helps those who are treated unjustly)\r\nOur prayer: Father, arise and fight for me this day, I have been molested, betrayed for righteousness sake, I have been crushed for integrity sake but I know you are my avenger, helper and defender  you will not allow the wicked crush me forever. Thank you Lord for coming to rescue me.\r\n\r\nOther text: Prov. 22:22-27, Psa 72:4  for your reading. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:22:19'),(47,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-16','YOU WILL DREAM GOOD DREAMS ','DAY: WED 16th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen.28:Il-12 â€œ...and lay down in that place to sleep. And he dreamed, and behold a ladder set up on the earth, and the top of it reached to heaven and behold the angels of God ascending and descending on it â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU WILL DREAM GOOD DREAMS \r\n\r\nSome folks usually see terrible creature like bulls, dogs,vultures chasing them. Some see themselves in the river or among dead people. Some dream and see themselves in pool of blood others see themselves having sex with strange people in the dream. All these are bad dreams. Just as Jacob never had a bad dream but a good one, where he saw angels of God ascending that was a heavenly dream. From today I strike out bad dreams in your life. May you never see terrible creature in your dream anymore. You are a child of God; your dreams should be good dreams. You should wake up with joy when you remember your dreams because they are good ones. From now you will never have bad dreams again; you belong to a good kingdom, so you must see good dreams. The devil has no right to threaten you with bad dreams is that alright? I declare you free from bad dreams. You shall dream good dream from now onward in Jesus Christ name!\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, disconnect me from today from terrible nightmares; let me see you and the beauty of your kingdom in my dreams. The devil can no more harass me in my dream in the name of Jesus Christ] pray (Amen!) \r\n\r\nOther text: Matt. 1 :20-24 for your reading. \r\n\r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:23:15'),(48,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-17',' Our Focus: SACRIFICING TO ESTABLISH A COVENANT','DAY: THURS 17th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOUR TEXT: Psa 50:5	â€œgather my saints together to me, those who have made covenant with me by sacrifice.â€\r\n\r\nOur Focus: SACRIFICING TO ESTABLISH A COVENANT\r\n\r\nToday I have this strong instruction in my spirit , it is a day to make a sacrifice to establish a covenant with God. I want everyone reading this piece today to take a step of faith, sacrifice something special to someone in need! Pick something that matters to you (remember sacrifice is something very precious to you, you give to someone in need of it)\r\nTake something that you love, it can be money, clothes, shoe, wrist watch, car, a phone or anything valuable, let the spirit of God lead you to someone in dear need of it and offer it to the person as unto the Lord. And it shall be for a covenant of righteousness for you. It shall establish a saintly spirit in you.\r\nA saint is someone who is not selfish but ready to make sacrifice for another person for the sake of God. The Lord takes delight in seeing us reach out to others with sacrifice of love. It is a great and acceptable deed to God. Its  a little way of reciprocating the sacrifice of his dearest son to us.\r\nThis is a special day of sacrifice not because you need someone to give you money but you are doing this today to wake the love of God in you. We are giving today not to get but to express love spirit in sacrifice to boost our saint nature in grace\r\n(sacrifice is when you give what matters to you to someone in need to express your deep love of God on the person you give)\r\nGo on your kneel, ask what and who to bless this morning with a sacrifice from you. As you bless a needy, God will be highly please with\r\n\r\nOther text: Heb 13:16, Luke 3:10-11, Prov 19:17 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:23:55'),(49,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-18','Our Focus: OFFER SPECIAL THANKS TO GOD','DAY: FRI 18th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOUR TEXT: Psa 50:14	â€œoffer to God thanksgiving and pay your vows to the most highâ€\r\n\r\nOur Focus: OFFER SPECIAL THANKS TO GOD\r\n\r\nThis morning I want you to offer special thanks to God, I want you first to thank God for certain evil that would have happened but did not. God averted certain evil on your life overnight. Can you remember your dream. Do you see what would have happened but averted and diverted? You need to thank him in a special way this morning. \r\nSecondly, I want you to thank him because something marvelous is about to happen in your life. I am sent to announce that to you, something great is on your way very soon! Can you thank him in advance? I see God rolling away your longtime reproach, a great door is opening for you. You are about crossing a boundary line, you are about to forget your hardship says the Lord. Your life is about to witness a sudden transformation. Kings are about to receive you. \r\nYour lifting is here but the way to it this morning is Thanks, your baby is coming soon, can you just thank him in a special way this morning. Go ahead and praise him, you can dance, you can kneel, you can roll in his presence to express your great thanks for what he is done as what He is about to do. Watch and see what follows as you obey this instruction.\r\n(Thanks is an expression of victory and prediction of his glory to come)\r\nOur Prayer: go ahead and thank him.\r\nOther text: Psa. 50:23 for your reading.\r\n','2018-05-20 00:24:43'),(50,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-19','Our Focus: FEEDING YOUR GENERATION ','\r\nOur text: Gen 30: 36 \"And he set three days journey between himself and Jacob; and Jacob Fed the rest of Laban\'s flocks. \r\n\r\nOur Focus: FEEDING YOUR GENERATION \r\n\r\nOne of the most powerful principles of success is to possess the ability to feed your generation. Giving people what they really need is a great favour you can ever show them. I watched how poultry fowls were fed one day, and the Lord said to me \'what if these fowls were neglected and not fed what do you think will happen to them?â€™ I said, Lord they will die. And he said to me you are right go and do likewise to the people around you, feed them with the word of life, or you will see them die spiritually over time if they are not fed. If you fail to feed your generation then you hand them over to destruction. God will hold you responsible. Be caring for the people around you, seek their welfare and you will save them from miserable life. When you give people what they need you invariably save their lives. May you be a savior by feeding those around you with what they dearly need! \r\n\r\nOur prayer: Father, give me the substance and the heart to feed the hungry flocks around me. Give me values that my generation needs and Let me never be comfortable seeing my generation hungry of what  I have! \r\n\r\nOther text: Isa. 58:1 0-11 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:25:31'),(51,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-20','Our Focus: YOU WILL DREAM GOOD DREAMS','DAY: SUN  20th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen.28:Il-12 â€œ...and lay down in that place to sleep. And he dreamed, and behold a ladder set up on the earth, and the top of it reached to heaven and behold the angels of God ascending and descending on it â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU WILL DREAM GOOD DREAMS \r\n\r\nSome folks usually see terrible creature like bulls, dogs,vultures chasing them. Some see themselves in the river or among dead people. Some dream and see themselves in pool of blood others see themselves having sex with strange people in the dream. All these are bad dreams. Just as Jacob never had a bad dream but a good one, where he saw angels of God ascending that was a heavenly dream. From today I strike out bad dreams in your life. May you never see terrible creature in your dream anymore. You are a child of God; your dreams should be good dreams. You should wake up with joy when you remember your dreams because they are good ones. From now you will never have bad dreams again; you belong to a good kingdom, so you must see good dreams. The devil has no right to threaten you with bad dreams is that alright? I declare you free from bad dreams. You shall dream good dream from now onward in Jesus Christ name!\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, disconnect me from today from terrible nightmares; let me see you and the beauty of your kingdom in my dreams. The devil can no more harass me in my dream in the name of Jesus Christ] pray (Amen!) \r\n\r\nOther text: Matt. 1 :20-24 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:26:44'),(52,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-21','Our Focus: TAKING OVER IN A STRANGE LAND ','DAY: MON  21st MAY., 2018 \r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 28:4 â€œAnd give thee the blessing of Abraham, to thee, and to thy seed with thee that thou mayest inherit the land where in thou art a stranger, which God gave unto Abraham.â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: TAKING OVER IN A STRANGE LAND \r\n\r\nAny land Abraham stepped in he took over. He succeeded in any strange land that he was noticeable. This grace I release upon your life will make you succeed among people of strange language. You will inherit the land where in you are a stranger. You will out shine your landlords. I see you rising to success beyond the people that host you. \r\nI hear this, the Lord has given us the land nobody can match us, we are going beyond all competitors. Our Divine connection is lifting us beyond competition. No one will match our success even in a strange land. We are destined for unbeatable success, Glory to God!\r\nOur Prayer: Lord Jesus cause me to inherit your blessing even in strange lands. Anywhere I find myself, I will succeed, your wisdom and grace will be upon me to overtake those that have been before me, I will succeed beyond my competitors; your glory on me will produce the difference (Amen!) \r\n\r\nOther text: Ps.105:10-11 for your reading. \r\n','2018-05-20 00:27:23'),(53,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-22','Our Focus: GOD WILL LEAD YOU TO WHERE YOU WILL SUCCEED ','DAY: TUES  22nd MAY., 2018 \r\nOur text: Gen 28: 2-3 â€œArise, go to Padanaram to the house Bethuel thy mother\' s father, and take a wife from thence of the daughter of Laban And God Almighty bless thee and make thee fruitful, and multiply thee, that thou mayest be multitude of people...â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL LEAD YOU TO WHERE YOU WILL SUCCEED \r\n\r\nIsaac instructed Jacob to go to Padanaram and to the house of Bethuel and there he became successful. Anywhere you will not succeed may your feet never step there. Any city or house you will enter and regret the day you were born, may you never go there, that your Amen is too weak, say it better (Amen). . The Almighty will order you to places where you will be celebrated. The Lord will take you to where your little effort shall produce multiple result and favour. God will direct you to where you will Flourish and not Languish or end in anguish! And I will like to conclude by telling you this confidently as God has led you to REFINER\'S HOUSE you will surely eat the bread of success and drink the wine of joy. Failure can never, never, never connect to you anymore. You have come to the place where your destiny will be EMPOWERED FOR SUCCESS PERFORMANCE watch it, it will soon happen for you!\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, thank you for leading me to the Refiner\'s House, a place where my potentials will rise to success and shine. Anywhere my favour is the rest of this week, help me locate it. Places that will help me succeed, help me locate it, no more futile struggles, you will order my steps to my place of exceptional favour in Jesus name.\r\n\r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:28:02'),(54,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-24','Our Focus: DON\'T BE WEARY OF YOUR LIFE','DAY: THURS  24th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen 27:46 â€œAnd Rebecca said to Isaac I am weary of my life because of the daughters of Hath ...â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: DON\'T BE WEARY OF YOUR LIFE \r\n\r\nFriends, nothing should make you weary of life. Life is a gift appreciate it, those who have lost it earnestly desire the second chance to it but it\'s unfortunate they couldn\'t. No matter what you are going through, life is still better than death. Think of the beautiful and wonderful dreams you have, you are yet to fulfill them. Why wish death for yourself? There is a privilege in life; change of Times and Seasons. You may be poor yesterday, don\'t be surprised you can be the richest tomorrow! You may be weak today, tomorrow may just be the day of your strength. Never undermine a minute before you; it can turn your entire course around. Don\'t be wearied. Something good and great will take place in your life today. You can make it! You will shine again. It\'s not over as long as there is breath in you. Today shall be a wonderful day for you. Can I hear your Amen! \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, I \'m sorry for getting tired of life because of what I faced in the past, let me see another (better) side of life as I step out today, turn every depression in my life to a good impression and let me begin to smile from now on in Jesus mighty name. \r\n\r\nOther text: In. 14:1-3 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:29:39'),(55,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-25',' Our Focus: RELOCATION FOR PROTECTION','\r\nDAY: FRI  25th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nOur text: Gen. 27:44-45 \"And tarry with him a few days until thy brotherâ€™s fury turn away; Until thy brother \'s anger turn away from thee and he forget that which thou hast done to him; then I will send and fetch thee from thence... \" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: RELOCATION FOR PROTECTION \r\n\r\nBy divine wisdom, God can relocate you to protect you from domestic adversaries. If you are surrounded by terrible people who aim at destroying you, God can move you to another location to keep you away from their sight. That is, why some times; it is not good to object transfer when it comes, it can be God\'s arrangement of hiding you from the wicked that want to destroy you. Sometimes when you are out of the sight of the wicked pe0ple, they feel relieve as they can\'t sight your success anymore.\r\n\r\nTheir thought of banning you may diffuse as they don\'t see you again. That was what happened to Jacob, his relocation caused Esau to forget harming him overtime. It is my prayer for you today that the Lord will hide you somewhere until your enemiesâ€˜ anger are diffused in Jesus Christ name. \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, relocate me to where my enemies cannot access me to destroy. Keep me away from their sight until they have forgotten their evil plan against me. I will not be meat to the enemies, my total trust in you will shield me and provide all round protection around my family. They will not succeed over us in Jesus name\r\n','2018-05-20 00:30:30'),(56,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-27','Our Focus: HATED BECAUSE OF THE BLESSING ','DAY: SUN  27th MAY., 2018\r\n\r\nour text: Gen. 27 :41 \"And Esau hated Jacob because of the blessing where with his father blessed him; and Esau said in his heart, the days of mourning for my father are at hand, and then will I slay my brother Jacob. \r\n\r\nOur Focus: HATED BECAUSE OF THE BLESSING \r\n\r\nHave you ever notice hatred from some people because of the blessing God gave you? Every time God blesses you some people will never be happy with you. The hatred comes because they don\'t have such a favour you have. Often time they plan evil against you to possibly get rid of you. Blessing usually attracts hatred from those who lack such blessing, so you have to be careful. \r\n\r\nIf you don\'t handle your blessing with great wisdom, you can be slain by those who lack such favour. The Lord will continue to protect you as he blesses you above your companions. Blessing without protection is dangerous. Ask the Lord to protect you as he also blesses you. \r\n\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, protect me as you bless me with your favour, everyone that hates me for the blessing and intend to slay me turn their counsel to foolishness over me. I declare myself covered with your blood therefore I AM UNTOUCHABLE. I will flourish and your divine security will be on me all through in Jesus name I pray (Amen) \r\n\r\nOther text: Gen. 31 :1 -2 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:31:17'),(57,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-28','Our Focus: 2 KINDS OF BLESSING ','\r\nOur text: Gen. 27:36-37 \" And Esau said, Hast thou not reserved a blessing for me? And Isaac answered and said unto Esau, Behold, I have made him thy lord, and all his brethren have I given to him for servants, \'and with corn and wine have I sustained him; and what shall I do now unto thee my Son?\" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: 2 KINDS OF BLESSING \r\n\r\nJacob received what I called THE SUB STANTIAL BLESSING, the blessing that carries a lot of Leadership grace and financial favour with Heaven\'s backing. \"Behold I have made him thy lord and with corn and wine have I sustained him Jacob got the blessing that is really loaded while Esau in great bitterness and grief asked for RESEREVED BLESSING \" And he said hast thou not a reserved blessing for me? Reserved blessing is not substantial. It is the blessing you beg for, it is not from the heart of the father, it is just from the mouth. May that not be your portion. You will not carry RESERVED BUT SUBSTANTIAL BLESSINGS. THE Lord will give you the blessing from his heart without you begging for it, that is substantial blessing it is your portion today!\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, bless me even when I didn\'t beg for it. Let your favour flow to my life from your heart and not just from your mouth, everlasting blessing is what Iâ€™ll receive from you today, my blessing will not only be for a period of time but as long as time in Jesus Christ name (Amen)\r\n\r\nOther text: Pro. 1 0:22 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:31:53'),(58,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-29','Our Focus: NO MAN SHALL TAKE AWAY YOUR BLESSING ','Our text: Gen 27: 34-35 \"And when Esau heard the words of his father, he cried with a great and exceeding bitter cry, and said unto his father, Bless me, even me also, 0 my father And he said, Thy brother came with subtlety, and hath taken away thy blessing\" \r\n\r\nOur Focus: NO MAN SHALL TAKE AWAY YOUR BLESSING \r\n\r\nThis is a very gracious prayer you need to pray for yourself this morning; No one will take away what belong to you. The blessing that is destined for you, may you never lose it to someone else due to carelessness. I remembered I planned a gift for someone and the person did not show up on time so I diverted the gift to another person. Just after I have done that the initial person I planned the gift for came, but I could not offer him as I have given it to another person. That was what happened to Esau. You will not lose what the Lord has for you to someone. It is a curse, whenever the blessing that is made for you is always diverted to someone else before your arrival. I rebuke that spirit in your life today your blessing will never pass you by in Jesus name! \r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, let not your blessings for me be diverted to anyone. Whatever I will do that will make me lose my favour to someone may I never do it. Help me to secure my blessings from you. Instead of losing my blessings to someone else rather transfer the blessings of unholy worshipers to me in Jesus name \r\n\r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:32:36'),(59,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-30','Our Focus: YOU ARE UN-CURSABLE! ','Our text. Gen. 27: 29b â€œ. Cursed be every one that curseth thee, and blessed be he that blesseth thee.â€ \r\n\r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU ARE UN-CURSABLE! \r\n\r\nWaow! What a blessing for you today, as you go out anyone that curses you is cursed. Whatever anyone speaks against you will befall them. It is dangerous to curse someone like you. You are the apple of his eyes. Anyone who touches you touches fire. No one is allowed to curse you. Anyone that curses you has just cursed his/her destiny. You are uncursable child of the ALMIGHTY GOD! Celebrate your Divine covering of grace whoever blesses you is also blessed. What a good ground you are. \r\nWhoever desires blessing should bless you and they shall reap it in return. You are so wonderful. Why not thank him for such a glorious favour on your life!\r\n\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Father, I\'m very grateful for such a blessing you put on me that makes me un-cursable for any man. Help me to always serve you so you can love me more, I will never give the devil an opportunity to take me from you. Thank you Lord for making me a soil of favour to whoever blesses me may I never disappoint you. \r\n\r\nOther text: PS. 1 05 :1 4-1 6 for your reading. \r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:33:10'),(60,NULL,'Apr - May (2018)','2018-05-31','Our Focus: LEADERSHIP BLESSING ','Our text: Gen. 2 7:29 â€œLet people serve thee, and nations bow down to thee; be Lord over thy brethren and let thy mother \'8 sons bow down to thee... â€ \r\n\r\nOur Focus: LEADERSHIP BLESSING \r\n\r\nThe Lord will make you the leader of your family, company and community Your voice shall count You will no more be underrated by anyone. The Lord is taking you up People shall seek your favour. The lord will give you what it takes to compel dignity from others. You are no more a slave but a brave man. No one will look down on you any more, you shall be a blessing to many and they shall respect you for that. When you are a blessing, then people will serve you. They will submit their leadership to you and that is the blessing God is giving today. People shall submit to you because of your tangible impact on their lives, may you be a blessing to people and they will serve you!\r\n\r\nOur Prayer: Lord, give me all It takes to bless my generation so I can secure the grace to lead them in righteousness. I shall be the head and not the tail of my clan. I will lead people to Christ and not away from you. Help me with the wisdom and grace I need to lead people so I wont be held responsible for their downfall in Jesus Christ name (A men). \r\n\r\nOther text: Det. 28:13 for your reading. \r\n\r\n\r\n','2018-05-20 00:33:53'),(64,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-01','YOU WILL HEAR GOD','DAY: Aug 1st Wed, 2018.	\r\nOar Text: Gen. 46:2 \"And God spoke unto Israel in the visions of the night and said, Jacob, Jacob. And he said here am Iâ€\r\n\r\nOur Focus: YOU WILL HEAR GOD\r\nWelcome and happy new month. As you begin this month, I command God\'s visitation for you in Jesus name.\r\nMy God will speak to you. He Will settle every confusion in your life. God will use someone today to clarify what He wants you to do.\r\nSome year ago, I am confused of life, until I met the servant of God, whom God used to speak to me on what He wants me to do and since then everything begins to work out well for me. My father in heaven will speak to you as you go out today, things will work out well for you.\r\nWisdom Lime: (When you Hear God, you experience success) \r\n\r\nPrayer: Father, speak to me redirect my life this month. Speak to me through your servant this month;\r\nhelp me to respond to your words.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:12:23'),(65,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-02','DON\'T BE AFRAID','DAY: Aug 2nd Thurs 2018.\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:3 â€œAnd he said l am God, the God of thy father; fear not to go down into Egypt; for I will there make of thee a great nationâ€\r\nOur Focus: DON\'T BE AFRAID\r\n\r\nDon\'t be afraid of taking that bold step. Go into that business, you will succeed. Those jobs that you desire is yours go after it; you will get it. Just be of good courage. Don\'t be afraid to Start that business with the small in your hand, soonest it shall be multiplied. My God is with you, He will not allow you to fail in that battle, victory is yours in Jesus name.\r\nThough you might be small now, you will soon be a great man/woman of your own time. You will be a leader of your field and men will bow to you.\r\nWisdom Lime: (Fear is killer of adventurous progress, don\'t submit to it)\r\nPrayer: Father, destroy every spirit of fear in my life in Jesus name. Endow me with grace to do what I cannot do, before, turn my small to great in Jesus name.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:13:00'),(66,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-03','MY GOD WILL GO WITH THEE','DAY: Aug 3rd Fri, 2018.\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:4 â€œI will go down with thee into j the Egypt; and 1 will also surely bring thee up again and Joseph shall put his hand upon thine eyesâ€\r\nOur Focus: MY GOD WILL GO WITH THEE\r\nAs you step out today, my God will go with you, as you come in He will surely be with you. When God go with you, guess what will happen! Favour of course! Favour of his protection, healing, breakthrough, deliverance, success, victory and lot more.\r\nBe assure that your journey shall be a safe one, no force can make you regret youâ€™re going out and your coming in today in the mighty name of Jesus Christ, it shall be well with you and your household. Just give God praise for going with you.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(When God go with you, no evil can come your way)\r\nPrayer: Father; never leave me alone, always go with me. Let my journeys be a smooth one today in Jesus name. Guide and protect me.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:13:24'),(67,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-04','GOD WILL DIGNIFY YOU','DAY: Aug 4th Sat 2018.\r\nOur Text:  Gen. 46:5 â€œAnd Jacob rose from Beersheba: and the sons of Israel carried Jacob their father, and their little ones, and their wives in the wagons which Pharaoh had sent to carry him\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL DIGNIFY YOU\r\nThe kind of vehicle that Jacob had never boarded was sent to him by Pharaoh. You could imagine how Jacob felt that day. The air-conditioner blew cool to his body together with a driver that was sent to drive him down to Joseph\'s place, what an honour! My God will dignify you. The kind of honour you have never enjoyed before will be given to you. You will be elevated to a higher level this month. Your family will also rejoice with your new family level.\r\nWisdom Lime: (When God dignify you, no force can nullify you)\r\nPrayer: Father, dignify me to a point I have never been before (amen).\r\n','2018-08-08 05:15:46'),(68,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-05','MOVING TO YOUR LAND OF ABUNDANCE','DAY: Aug 5th Sun 2018.\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:6 â€œAnd they took their cattle, and their goods, which they had gotten in the land of Canaan, and came to Egypt, Jacob and his seed with himâ€\r\nOur- Focus MOVING TO YOUR LAND OF ABUNDANCE\r\nCanaan was full of famine no food, no money, everywhere was dry, the only land you can find food was Egypt, on this note a lot of people travelled to Egypt including Jacob in search of food where food was in abundance.\r\nYou have been experiencing famine, poverty, dryness. My God said I should announce to you, that, you are moving from that dry land to your land of abundance where you will have more than enough for yourself and family. You will no longer sell your belonging for food again in Jesus name. Tell yourself; am moving to my land of abundance, 3 times say bye-bye to poverty, bye-bye to famine, bye-bye to failure, bye-bye to stagnation, am moving to my land of abundance where anything I do will flourish.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(God will always move His children,\r\nfrom better to best level)\r\nPrayer: Father, move me to my land of abundance. Put a stop to scarcity and lack in my life in Jesus name.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:16:07'),(69,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-06','GODâ€™S FAVOUR WILL EXTEND TO YOUR SEEDS','DAY: Aug 6th Mon 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:7 â€œHis sons, and his son\'s sons with him his daughters and his son\'s daughters, and all his seed brought he with him into Egyptâ€\r\nOur Focus: GODâ€™S FAVOUR WILL EXTEND TO YOUR SEEDS\r\nMay God never give you a favour that will not extend to your seeds. God\'s favour was so much on Joseph that he was able to take care of himself, his family and extended family.\r\nThat favour was too much for him alone. That is the kind of favour am asking God to give you. Your grandchildren will partake of that favour in your life in Jesus name.\r\nThrough you, every member of your house will be liberated from the spirit of poverty. Your seed will not be bound anymore. God will use you to change their level to relocate them from famine to abundance from lack of surplus from sorrow to Joy in the mighty name of Jesus. I see that happening for you.\r\nWisdom Lime: (Favour that does not extend beyond you is a limited favour)\r\nPrayer: Father, let your favour upon me be extended to my grandchildren, let it be too much for me alone.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:16:35'),(70,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-07','YOUR MANASSEH WILL BE BORN','DAY: Aug 7th Tues 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:20a And unto Joseph in the land of | I	Egypt were horn Manasseh and Ephraim\"\r\nOur Focus: YOUR MANASSEH WILL BE BORN\r\nThe meaning of Manasseh is God caused me to forget my past. Something will happen in your life that will make you to forget how you suffered, how you couldn\'t eat, how you were been sent out of school, how your creditor disgraced you, how the NEPA disconnected your light because you were unable to pay. God will elevate you to a higher realm and comfort you on every side. You have been seeing people with their cars, fine houses, beautiful wives and husband, good job and you wonder, why is my own different from these people. My God said I should tell you that your future is very bright. Don\'t cry again, don\'t be devastated, very soon your story will change and you will forget your past. Manasseh will be born for you and people will rejoice with you. Shout my Manasseh will be born in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime: (The arrival of your favour terminates the suffering pain of your past suffering)	\r\nPrayer: Father, let my Manasseh be born. Do something in my life that will make me forget my past, give me a better today.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:16:55'),(71,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-08',' YOU SHALL BE FRUITFUL','DAY: Aug 8th Wed 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:20a \"And unto Joseph in the land were born Manasseh and Ephraimâ€\r\nOUR FOCUS: YOU SHALL BE FRUITFUL\r\nEphraim means fruitfulness in the land of your affliction. You have been suffering over the years, you can\'t eat what you want, can\'t pay your children fee, the job you are waiting for is yet to click, the business is not yielding much, these has cause men to look down on you and molest you. Now listen, you story is about to change. That same land where you have been afflicted, where you have suffered will soon become a fruitful land for you.\r\nIt does not take God anything to change your story. He will make you fruitful and bless you mightily in that land. People that pass by your side with their cars and will not lift you will soon see you in your car, in fact better than theirs. Your business that has been down will suddenly star yielding increase for you. That promotion that has not being affected will be done and your salary will increase. People will not recognize you, just like Joseph was not recognized by his brethren. My God will make you fruitful in the land where you have been afflicted in Jesus name. It is so sweet to succeed in the land where people have written you off. Your affliction will be written off in Jesus name (amen).\r\nWisdom Lime: (God\'s affection will rule out your afflictions)\r\nPrayer: Father bless me in the land of my affliction. Let me be fruitful in the land where I have suffered.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:17:45'),(72,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-09','YOUR LEVEL WILL ATTRACT MEN TO YOU','DAY: Aug 9th Thurs 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:27 \"And the sons of Joseph which were born him in Egypt, were two sons; all the souls of the house of Jacob, which came in Egypt, were three score and tenâ€\r\nOur Focus: YOUR LEVEL WILL ATTRACT MEN TO YOU\r\nWhen you are in low level in life, no one wants to make friend with you but when God place you in a higher position, everybody wants to be your friend. Higher level attracts men, both old and young. God will put you in a higher place of life in Jesus name, where, men will be attracted to you.\r\nPeople want to come around you, because they know you are a great man of your life. When you open your gate, you will see men line up to see you. God have something in you that can also change their level. My God will take you there. You will no longer watch people going to higher men but you will see people coming to you for help in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(Your level of success will determine your level of relationship)\r\nPrayer:	Father, take me to the highest place of life. Let me no longer remain in low level life; let my position attract men to me.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:18:10'),(73,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-10','GOD WILL DIRECT YOU TO YOUR GOSHEN','DAY: Aug 10th Fri 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:28 â€œAnd he sent Judah before him unto Joseph, to direct his face unto Goshen; and they came into the land of Goshenâ€\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL DIRECT YOU TO YOUR GOSHEN\r\nI was going to work one certain morning, on the way to my place of work, I met someone who directed me back to another way, few minutes, and we discovered that everyone on that road was badly wounded by some rioters. Imagine what would have happened to me if I had followed that way. I would have been killed or wounded probably lost any part of my body. This morning as you go out, my God will direct you to where your life will be safe. You will not fall into the hands of bad boys that will harm or take any of your belongings. God will direct you to Goshen where your security is guaranteed (both you and everything that belongs to you). Your security is sure in Goshen.\r\nWisdom Lime:	Prosperity without security is adversity \r\nPrayer: Father, direct me to Goshen where my security is guaranteed. Let me not remain in Egypt where there is no security.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:21:35'),(74,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-11','YOUR ENEMIES SHALL SEE YOU UP','DAY: Aug 11th Sat 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:29a \"And Joseph made ready his chariot, and went up to meet Israel his father, to Goshen, and presented himself unto himâ€\r\nOur Focus: YOUR ENEMIES SHALL SEE YOU UP\r\nThose that concluded that you are dead will suddenly realize you are alive. They said your own has finished, no one will hear you or see you again. They will one day tune to their TV and discover you are being interviewed. They want to hear you are dead and hear you are nobody but reverse will be the case for your enemies. They will see your wife more beautiful than theirs, they will see your fine cars, they will see your beautiful and handsome children, they will see them studying abroad, and they will see your body guards and drivers. God will cause your enemies to see you contrary to their expectations in Jesus name (amen).\r\nWisdom Lime: (When God lift you up, He also drifts your enemies down)	\r\nPrayer: Father, let me ride on chariot. Let me be up and not down in my carrier in Jesus Christ name I prayed.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:21:57'),(75,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-12','YOU WILL SHED TEARS OF JOY','DAY: Aug 12th Sun 2018.\r\n\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:29b â€œAnd he fell on his neck, and wept on his neck a good while \"\r\nOur Focus: YOU WILL SHED TEARS OF JOY\r\nI prophesy tears of joy for you this month. Something will happen that will make you cry for joy. You will see yourself in place where you never expect, handle the money you have never handled in your life. You will be expecting to see your monthly circle but will not come, behold it has stayed says the Lord of Host. You will see yourself in a place where you never dream to be in the next 10 years. You will suddenly be call upon for an interview which will turn your world around. Get set to shed the tears of joy.\r\nEnemies have concluded that they are through with you, they have finalized you can be anything again, behold, they will see you where no one in their generation have never been and you will see them and shed tears of joy.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(Tears of joy are an expression of encounter with miracle)\r\nPrayer: Father, do something in my life that will make me shed tears of joy. Turn my sorrow to laughter.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:22:31'),(76,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-13','YOUR SUCCESS WILL KILL YOUR ENEMIES','DAY: Aug 13th Mon 2018.\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:30a â€œAnd Israel said unto Joseph, now let me dieâ€\r\nOur Focus: YOUR SUCCESS WILL KILL YOUR ENEMIES\r\nI noticed when people come for prayer and counseling and said, pastor â€œpray for me, I want my enemies to die, because they are behind my predicamentâ€.\r\nSometimes God kills them. Other time he spares them so they can see your success. Success kills your enemies faster than anything else. It is good for your enemies to be alive and see you succeeding. I will not be happy am succeeding after my enemies\' death, no let them be alive and see what God can do.\r\nI command your success to come now in Jesus name. As it comes, your enemies will prefer death to life. Success that will make your enemies commit suicide will come your way this month in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(The best way to torment your enemies is for them to see your success)\r\nPrayer: Father, let my success kill my enemies, so they will not be able to withstand my success.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:25:05'),(77,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-14',' YOU WILL LIVE','DAY: Aug 14th Tues 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 46:30b â€œSince I have seen thy face because thou art yet aliveâ€\r\nOur Focus: YOU WILL LIVE\r\nThe will of God for you is to live long and fulfill your purpose on the earth while the devil has come to steal, kill and to destroy. I release judgmental fire upon anyone that wants to kill you before your time in Jesus name. They are free to plan it, but all I know is that their counsel shall not stand, my God will keep and shield you from any attack of the devil that might want you dead.\r\nDeath is not your portion; you will live and be a star in your field in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime: (If your living is prospective to God, then He gives you his protective device)\r\nPrayer:	Father, keep and shield me from any power that might want to cut my days short. Let my enemies take the death plan against me.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:25:29'),(78,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-15','YOUR FAMILY IS COMING OUT OF SUFFERING','DAY: Aug 15th  Wed 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text; Gen. 47:1 â€œWhen Joseph came and told Pharaoh) and said, my father and my brethren, and their flocks, and their herds, and all that they have, are come out of the land of Canaan and behold, they are in the land of Goshen\"\r\nOur Focus:	YOUR FAMILY IS COMING OUT OF SUFFERING\r\nCanaan in our text represents hunger, hardship or famine. Joseph brought them out of Goshen where they can enjoy wealth and other necessary favour.\r\nThis year your family will move out of Canaan of suffering, you are all coming out of terrible hardship, you are coming out of lacks (famine) and you will enter God\'s abundance.\r\nHardship affects the peace of a family; it is very difficult to experience peace in any family where hardship prevails. When there is hunger in your family love cannot flow. The family will be moody as the necessities are lacking. I pray for your family this morning God will move you out of suffering to abundance in the mighty name of Jesus Christ. I curse every spirit of hardship in your family in Jesus Christ name.\r\nWisdom Lime: (Hardship destroys family peace hut God\'s favour increases your joy)\r\nPrayer: Father, move my family out of the land of hardship to where your favour will be available for us always. Take us to a place of surplus where we shall eat our bread without scarcity.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:25:50'),(79,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-16','YOU WILL STAND BEFORE KINGS','DAY: Aug 16th Thurs 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:2 â€œAnd he (Joseph) took some of his brethren even five men, and presented them unto Pharaohâ€\r\nOur Focus: YOU WILL STAND BEFORE KINGS\r\nGOD used Joseph to take his brethren to King (Pharaoh), they would have never stand before Pharaoh except for Joseph\'s sake.\r\nGood people can be ladder to greatness. Greatness in life is achievable through good people like Joseph. I also want to pray for you, this morning, God will raise you to a point you will help others to greatness.\r\nGod will make you the Joseph of your family and that will help others to stand before KINGS!\r\nYou shall be an AGENT TO GREATNESS. I see God using you to lift men to a place they never believe they can attain in life in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lithe: (Good people are ladder to greatness connect to them and they will help you up)\r\nPrayer: Father, make me an instrument to lift others to greatness. Use me to lift others to greatness. Use me to bring-someone to a point of standi ng with kings in Jesus name I prayed.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:26:29'),(80,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-17',' GOD WILL GIVE YOU AN OCCUPATION','DAY: Aug 17th  Fri 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text:  Gen. 47:3 â€œAnd Pharaoh said unto his brethren, what is your occupation? Thy servants are shepherds, both we also and our fathers \"\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL GIVE YOU AN OCCUPATION\r\nOne of the questions people always ask you in life is WHAT IS YOUR OCCUPATION? In other words, what is your work? Someone who has no job will be ashamed of answering such question.\r\nIf you have an occupation, you take pleasure in responding to the question. I pray for all those who are idle or jobless, God will provide you with an occupation. You will no longer be idle, so you can stand boldly anywhere and tell people your job. I remove the shame of joblessness in your life. Few days from now, my God will engage you with a work and your idleness will be over. You will have an occupation soon in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime: (Occupation is what you do to earn your living, without it life becomes difficult) \r\n\r\nPrayer: Father, bless me with an occupation so I can earn J resources to take care of my needs in life. Grant me a favour of work soon, so I can give you the glory... (Amen)\r\n','2018-08-08 05:27:14'),(81,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-18','THERE SHALL NOT BE FAMINE IN OUR LAND','DAY: Aug 18th Sat 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:4 â€œ...for thy servants has no pasture for their flocks; for the famine is sore in the land of Canaan... \"\r\nOur Focus: THERE SHALL NOT BE FAMINE IN OUR LAND\r\nFamine will have no hold in our land as it did in Canaan. The presence of Joseph made it impossible for famine to reign in Egypt. Wherever A GODLY AND WISE MAN is, famine cannot reign.\r\nRefiners our presence in this land will not allow famine (hardship) to reign. Wherever DEDICATED PEOPLE are, abundance reigns. People with insight, destroys the plight of hardship.\r\nI prophesy from today, famine will never reign in our land. The wisdom of God in us will handle it. Joseph\'s wisdom bailed Egypt from famine; the wisdom of God in our father here in Refiners House will terminate famine in our life. Hardship will never reign in Refiners House; we shall command abundance in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime: (The wisdom of investment destroys the grip of hardship. The more you handle poverty)\r\nPrayer: Father, give me the grace to follow the wise counsel of my father so 1 can escape famine in my house.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:27:38'),(82,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-19','GOD WILL SATISFY YOU WITH HIS BEST!','DAY: Aug 19th Sun 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:5-6 â€œAnd Pharaoh spoke unto Joseph saying, thy father and thy brethren are come unto thee. The land of Egypt is before thee; in the best of the land make thy father and thy brethren to dwell...â€\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL SATISFY YOU WITH HIS BEST!\r\nAs you go out this morning, my God will bless you with his BEST, you will receive a peculiar favour today. It shall be nothing less than the best. You will succeed in that land. You will be rated among the best in your class, career and in your business.\r\nI pray for you again, you shall be among the best of the land. You shall take the lead, you will perform excellently, and you will not fail as you step out today, THE BEST OF THE LORD IS YOUR PORTION. Go and reap God\'s BEST for your life today. You will return with a song of joy today in Jesus Christ name!\r\nWisdom Lime:	(God\'s children deserve the best of the land because their God is the landlord)\r\n Prayer: Father, satisfy me with your best favour as I go out today, bless me on every side. \r\n','2018-08-08 05:28:01'),(83,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-20','YOU WILL SEE AND TASTE YOUR CHILDREN SUCCESS','DAY: Aug 20th  Mon 2018.\r\n\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:7 â€œThen Joseph brought his father Jacob in and presented him before Pharaoh...â€\r\nOur Focus:	YOU WILL SEE AND TASTE YOUR CHILDREN SUCCESS\r\nI remember a man who died on the day of his daughter\'s wedding. He did not see the end of the wedding ceremony nor live to taste his daughter\'s success.\r\nI also recalled the mother of the president of a country died, the very week her son assumes office as the president of that country. How I wish she stay a little longer, not just to see her son became the president, but to also taste the pleasure in the arena of presidency.\r\nIt is possible to see your children\'s success and not taste of it before death will come. 1 stand in my prophetic calling this morning to rebuke that for you. You will not only SEE your children\'s success, you will also TASTE from their success. As Jacob enjoys his son\'s success in Egypt so you shall enjoy your children\'s success in the mighty name of Jesus Christ.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(Seeing and tasting your children\'s success is the pleasure of real parental success)\r\nPrayer: Father, keep me alive to see and taste my children\'s success, let me not die without tasting the success of my children in Jesus Christ name I prayed.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:28:22'),(84,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-21','THE GOD OF JACOB WILL BLESS YOU TODAY','DAY: Aug 21st Tues 2018.\r\n\r\n\r\nOur Focus: THE GOD OF JACOB WILL BLESS YOU TODAY\r\nGod blessed Jacob with 3 unusual blessing, they are: the blessing of overtaking, the blessing of increase and the blessing of protection.\r\nJacob overtook Esau though Esau was the elder brother. You will overtake those who started before you. When the blessing of Jacob is upon you, you carry overtaking grace. You will outweigh your competitors in Jesus name.\r\nJacob increased immensely the little substance of Laban. Every little resources in your hand will increase mightily today in the name of Jesus Christ. Jacob enjoyed the blessing of divine protection, not even Laban could harm him. When he intended to do so God warned him not to touch Jacob.\r\nI release that blessing upon you, anyone that attempt to touch you will receive DIVINE WARNING and if they touch you God will strike them death! Today, no devil will be able to touch you, as you go out you are totally secured under his blessing of protection. Shout I AM UNTOUCHABLE TO ANY DEVIL IN JESUS CHRISTNAME!\r\nWisdom Lime:	(When the God of Jacob blesses you, you experience mysterious overtaking, increase and protection)\r\nPrayer:	Father, bless me with your blessings today as I go out, give me the grace to overtake my competitors, increase my little substance and protect me from all evil in Jesus Christ name I prayed.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:28:54'),(85,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-22','HOW OLD ARE YOU?','DAY: Aug 22nd Wed 2018.\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:8 â€œPharaoh asked him â€œHow old are you?\" \r\nOur Focus: HOW OLD ARE YOU?\r\nWhat a question the Holy Ghost is asking you this morning, how old are you? Now this question is in two dimensions. First, how old are you in the world i.e. biological age; are you 30,40, 45 or 55 years old?\r\nSecondly, the Holy Spirit is asking how old are you in the Lord? I.e. spiritual age. When did you give your life to Christ, if at all you have? You know what, if you are 100 years old biologically and you have not given your life to Christ, it simply means you are living a wasted life. Our age in Christ is more relevant than our age in the world. Spending 50 years on earth without Christ is one of the greatest potential lost you can bring to your life. Your age in Christ is what matters. Don\'t let your years go without Christ; if you pass on, to the other side without Jesus, you have lived a wasted life. Please dedicate your life to Christ this morning, choose to love Him, welcome Him to your life and follow His instruction daily and you will live a meaningful life. Your years on earth will not be wasted in Jesus name I pray.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(It is not how long you live on earth that matters, but now long you are in Christ that is the ultimate)\r\nPrayer: Father, let me live in you than I live in the world. Let my spiritual age be far above my earthly age. Let me not just count days but let me be committed to you.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:29:12'),(86,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-23','YOU WILL OUT-LIVE YOUR FATHERS',' \r\nDAY: Aug 23rd Thurs 2018.\r\n\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen 47:9 â€œAnd Jacob said to Pharaoh, the years of my pilgrimage are a hundred and thirty. My years have been few and difficult and they do not equal the years of the pilgrimage of my fathersâ€ (NIV)\r\nOur Focus: YOU WILL OUT-LIVE YOUR FATHERS\r\nJacob could not live equal or beyond the day of his father because of polygamy. He married two wives that brought a lot of conflict to his life. This consequently shortened his years below his father\'s age.\r\nAbraham died at 175 years, while Isaac died at 180 years but Jacob lived for just 147 years. The trouble of polygamy afflicted his joy which reduced his life span.\r\nOne of the secrets of long life is to be contented with whatever God has given you. Be satisfied with your wife. Don\'t think of adding another woman to your life, or you cause problem for your life. Don\'t destroy your life by marrying another woman. Be satisfied with that one and you will live long in Jesus name. You will live longer than your fathers, as you remain Satisfy with what God has given you.\r\n\r\nWisdom Lime: (The more you are satisfied with God\'s gift, the longer you live)\r\nPrayer: Father, help me to be satisfied with your gift for my life, let me not destroy myself through covetousness in Jesus name I prayed!\r\n','2018-08-08 05:29:34'),(87,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-24','NEVER GO OUT FROM HIS PRESENCE','DAY: Aug 24th Fri 2018.\r\n\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 49:10 â€œThen Jacob blessed Pharaoh and went out from his presence \"\r\nOur Focus: NEVER GO OUT FROM HIS PRESENCE\r\nAnytime I sit with my wife and we keep talking, I never want the conversation to end. I deeply enjoy our interactions. We talk very interesting and inspiring issues. Sometimes; if we have to depart for our official duties, I feel we should not depart for that little period we missed each other.\r\nThis is how we should enjoy God\'s presence and never desire to lose it for a moment. In God\'s presence, there is great love, as well amazing wisdom. If you sit in God\'s presence always, you walk in love and you carry exceptional wisdom.\r\nI learn a lot of great ideas in God\'s presence so much that I never want to lose him for a moment, without his presence I feel boring, insecure and lonely. When you lose God\'s presence, life becomes boring; you will as well be insecured and lonely.\r\nI pray for you today, you will not go out of his presence. 2 things can make you lose the presence of God, when you are SINFUL, when you make SIN your lifestyle, you lose his presence (Ps. 15). Secondly, when you become very ungrateful, you lose God\'s presence (Ps. 100:4) people that stay in God\'s presence are those with grateful heart, those who thank Him for everything in life. They never murmur against God irrespective of what happens to them. I pray for you today, God will bless you with a grateful heart so you can stay long in his presence in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime: (God\'s presence is what gives our lives essence)\r\nPrayer: Father, help me never to lose your presence; it is the essence for my life.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:30:59'),(88,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-25','GOD WILL ARRANGE THE BEST PLACE FOR YOU','DAY: Aug 25th Sat 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:11 \"So Joseph settled his father and his brothers in Egypt and gave them property in the best part of the land, the district of Ramases, as Pharaoh directed\" (NIV)\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL ARRANGE THE BEST PLACE FOR YOU\r\nWhen I was a little boy, my mother will share meat or other edible items and call us the children to choose, however, it is done j according to our age. The eldest will chose before it gets to the \\ youngest.\r\nYou know what, I was always given the privilege to choose first j because I was the FIRST MALE child, my mother gave me that preferential treatment guess what, I usually chose the best before others will take theirs. That is the work of favour. Joseph chose the best part for his father and brethren in Egypt, because they are connected to him.\r\nI prophesy for you today, God will arrange the best place for you, your result shall be the best, your proposal shall be the best, and your children shall be the best in their school. Everything about you shall be the best, others can now have the remaining, shout THE BEST is my PORTION IN THE NAME OF JESUS CHRIST.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(When you have the BEST, contenders can have the REST)\r\nPrayer: Father, bless me with your best from today, let your favour flow to my life beyond any Egyptian around me in Jesus Christ name I prayed. \r\n','2018-08-08 05:31:16'),(89,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-26','BREADWINNER','DAY: Aug 26th Sun 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:12 â€œJoseph also provided his father and his brothers and his entire father\'s household with food, according to the number of their childrenâ€\r\nOur Focus: BREADWINNER\r\nI enlist you among the bread-winner of life. As Joseph became the bread-winner and sustained his father, brothers and his entire household, so God will use you to sustain your father\'s house.\r\nBread-winners are elevated persons in diving favour with the ability to sustain others comfortably. God will elevate you to a point where you will sustain a lot of people, especially your family members.\r\nBREAD-WINNERS are people no one believes they could amount to anything. They are brought up in a harsh condition. You could hardly see any sign of greatness in them at the initial stage of their lives. They pass through a lot of trials but at last their star comes to lime light. One wonderful thing I will not but mention about them, they are people with unusual compassion to help others. They have human feelings. They care for the needy. They derive exceptional joy in helping their fellows. People who lack such compassionate heart can never be BREAD-WINNERS.\r\nI pray for you this morning; the Lord will make you one among THE BREAD-WINNERS OF LIFE as you carry a compassionate heart in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(The keys to becoming a BREAD-WINNER are your readiness to pass through tough time and readiness to be a blessing to others)\r\nPrayer: Father, elevate me to the point of the bread-winner of my family so I can help others out of their predicament\r\n','2018-08-08 05:31:41'),(90,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-27','I TERMINATE FAMINE IN OUR REGION ',' \r\nDAY: Aug 27th  Mon  2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:13 â€œThere was no food, however, in the whole region because the famine is severe, both Egypt and Canaan wasted away because of famine \"\r\nOur Focus: I TERMINATE FAMINE IN OUR REGION \r\nFamine is a severe and critical moment of need that could lead to death: terrible experience like malnutrition, prostitution, frustration and lamentation come with famine!\r\nSo, it is an experience we should never allow in our region, if you suffer famine and God does not intervene, you can deny the faith. You can even curse God or stop coming to church. Oh, what a miserable thing. Famine is what we must pray against this morning, whatever will bring terrible hardship to our region Refiners House we reject it in Jesus mighty name, can your amen be louder? Famine will never occur in your family this year. Famine comes as a result of breaking the laws of God. If we provoke God to anger as stated in (Deut. 8: 15-20), He sends famine. Ah! It is my prayer for you this morning, whatever you will do that will provoke the anger of God, may you never do it. Every evil attitude that can make God\'s favour cease from our region, we will never do it in Jesus name. Our church will never know famine. God will never deny us the supply of spiritual food. The word of God (our food) will be mightily available in our church in Jesus name. There shall not be famine in our region in Jesus Christ name.\r\nWisdom Lime:	(Disobedience is the facilitator of famine, may we not tread on that track)\r\nPrayer:  Father, help us to obey your voice so that rain of your favour will not cease in our lives. Let famine never strike in our region in Jesus Christ name.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:32:02'),(91,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-28','YOU WILL COMMAND UNUSUAL WEALTH','DAY: Aug 28th Tues 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:14 \"Joseph collected all the money that was to be found in Egypt and Canaan in payment for the. grain they were buying and he brought it to Pharaoh\'s house \" (NIV)\r\nOur Focus:	YOU WILL COMMAND UNUSUAL WEALTH\r\nMost people believe money is very difficult to get but that is not true. Money is very easy to get, if only you know the secret of money. Money respects certain principles; let me share some with you. If you want to make money in life, have a needful product you can sell. Money doesn\'t come to people who are doing nothing but people doing something needful to humanity. If you can offer goods and services that are major necessities of life, you will make a lot of money where others are complaining of poverty. Joseph made a lot of money in the midst of famine. He had grains (food) which was a dare need, so he made money. It is my prayer for you, God will give you goods and services your environment need, and money will come to you immensely. You can\'t be poor if you have NEEDFUL GOODS AND SERVICES to offer. As you go out today, you will make a lot of money in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime: (Where you find the NEEDS of people, they will lay their SEED (money) at your feet)\r\nPrayer:	Father, bless my going out today with your favour, let my goods and services be highly patronized, so I cart secure your financial favour, I will return with your blessings today in Jesus name I prayed.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:32:20'),(92,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-29','YOUR MONEY WILL NOT FINISH','DAY: Aug 29th  Wed 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:15 \"When the money of the people of Egypt and Canaan was gone, all Egypt came to Joseph and said, â€œgive us food why should we also die before your eyes? Our money is used upâ€\r\nOur Focus: YOUR MONEY WILL NOT FINISH\r\nMoney is a dynamic force. It requires great wisdom to sustain money. If you lack wisdom, even, if you are given money you will still come back to poverty. If you don\'t know how to handle money, you will use it up. Money flows to people who do not spend everything that comes their ways.\r\nThey plough back some part of the money. Just as a farmer who does not eat up his whole harvest. He keeps some seed for replanting. Once you make money don\'t spend all try to invest. Honour God with your tithe, so He can grant you favour to make more money. Then buy things that can yield more money for you. Instead of using money for birthday or burial ceremonies, why not use the money for a business.\r\nThere is no kingdom sense in spending for birthday or burial when you don\'t have any investment. Whatever takes money away from you unnecessarily will bind you to poverty. Some of the money you waste on unnecessary journey can be invested in a nice small-scale business, which will later bring back further wealth to you.\r\nMany people remain poor because they use money carelessly. Money respects helpers and investors. If you are good in helping others, as well goods in re-investing, you can never be bound to poverty! I release the grace on you to help others from your little resources and to always plough back and you will never lack money in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime: (Those who help others and re-invest money\' never go down financially)	\r\nPrayer: Father, grant me the grace to help and to always re-invest. So, poverty will not get rid of my finance.\r\n','2018-08-08 05:32:41'),(93,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-30','GOD WILL USE YOU TO SAVE SOMEONE FROM DEATH',' \r\nDAY: Aug 30th Thurs 2018.\r\n\r\nOur Text: Gen. 47:15b â€œ...give us food, why should we die before your eyes?â€\r\nOur Focus: GOD WILL USE YOU TO SAVE SOMEONE FROM DEATH\r\nI release this grace on you this morning, DEATH REVOKING GRACE. Whoever identifies with you will not die before your eyes. God will use you to rescue someone from untimely death.\r\nGod used Joseph for the people and they never died. I put the grace on you to rescue someone from dying. People, who thought life is over for them will receive new hop through you.\r\nYou will restore the hope of someone today. Someone will call you in pain and God will use you to give life back to the person. You are a deliverer. You will rescue someone from dying. The power is giving to you. No one will be helpless where you are, God will use you to give them the way out. You will rescue the hopeless in Jesus name.\r\nWisdom Lime: (Saviours are men with divine capacity to rescue the helpless, hopeless and the useless back to the point of success and that is, who you are)\r\nPrayer:	Father, use me to rescue the destitute, let my presence bring life to the hopeless. Give me all it takes to revive the dying ones around me...in Jesus Christ name 1 prayed!\r\n','2018-08-08 05:33:02'),(94,NULL,'Aug - Sept (2018)','2018-08-31','SPECIAL PRAYER FROM THE MAN OF GOD','DAY: Aug 31th Fri 2018.\r\n\r\n\r\nSPECIAL PRAYER FROM THE MAN OF GOD\r\nThis is a Special Prayer for someone; my God will bless you with unusual favour this quarter. I prophesy safety in your going out and coming. Every evil designed for you has failed, I nullify it in the mighty name of Jesus Christ!\r\nMy God shall supply all your needstoday. You will never beg to eat. You will never know sickness as you close this month. Everyone in your house will step  the month ahead successfully.\r\nFavour will come your way to the last minute of this month. You will never experience sorrow! You will not weep. Thieves will never know your house, office or business premises. You will not regret ending this month. You will experience victory in your dreams. Every demonic agent that attempts you will CRASH!\r\nYour business will flourish. You will receive your promotion letter. You will be celebrated and you will step the month ahed with GREAT TESTIMONIES says the LORD of Host!\r\nGo ahead and thank him in advance for  the New month ahead!\r\n','2018-08-08 05:33:25'),(95,'DAILY FIRE...jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-01','GOD WILL DO GREAT AND WONDERFUL THINGS FOR YOU','<p>Our Text: &quot;For you are great and perform wonderful deeds&rdquo; (Psa. 86:10)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: GOD WILL DO GREAT AND WONDERFUL THINGS FOR YOU</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Good news for you brother/sister. This day, God is set to do something wonderful for you. I can hear it again for you get set, for something great and wonderful will take place in your life today.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No devil can stand or stop what God is set to do in your life today. It is a day of miracles for you. God has a special gift for you whom today is your BIRTHDAY! You are blessed with the blessing of greatness, you will never die untimely favour is all around you in Jesus name! Appreciate God for seeing you through this month.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (When God is at work, wonders will Follow you)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, do something great for me today; let me see your mighty hand at work in my life this day. Do what no one can do forme! (Amen)</p>','2019-07-04 00:39:24'),(96,'DAILY FIRE..(1).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-02','YOU WILL BE LIFTED BY YOUR FATHER\'S FAVOUR','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;And Jacob said to Joseph .. beyond what I have given your brothers, I am giving you an extra portion of the land that I took from the Amorites with my sword and bow&rdquo; (Gen. 18:21-22)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOU WILL BE LIFTED BY YOUR FATHER\'S FAVOUR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jacob gave Joseph a blessing beyond his brothers he was lifted by the father\'s favour. I see you rising on the wings of yourfather\'s blessing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When God blesses you Beyond others you will surely rise beyond them. This month, you will rise beyond many. You will overtake many you will emerge the best. You will be wonderfully favoured. You will succeed above others. You will never fail or fall this month. I can see you on an extra ordinary point this month. The blessing of your father in this Ministry will set you up above others in this city. You are lifted by Hisfavourthis month.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (The father\'s blessing takes you farther in Life)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, lift me beyond others this month through your favour on my life and the prophetic blessing of my father.</p>','2019-07-03 02:49:00'),(97,'DAILY FIRE..(2).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-03','YOU SHALL NOT BE IN DARKNESS','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;And Jacob called unto his sons, and said, gather yourselves together, that I may tell you that which shall befall you in the last days&rdquo; (Gen. 49:1)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOU SHALL NOT BE IN DARKNESS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you are in darkness you cannot see, you can\'t move, you are afraid, you are not safe, you are in danger. This month of July shall be your month of light in Jesus name. Darkness will not cover you. Everything that has been in darkness shall come to light in your life. You will understand things that have been confusing to you. Hidden agenda of the devil over your life shall be revealed in Jesus name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our nation Nigeria shall enter into another greater light. God will be enthroned in this nation. Every secret of the Devil and his agent over this nation shall be uncovered. The nation will move forward and every evil person will die a terrible death. Wisdom Lime: (Your encounter with light will terminate yourplight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, uncover every secret agenda of the devil over my family and this nation. Destroy their plan and let your light shine in my life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2019-07-03 02:48:45'),(98,'DAILY FIRE..(3).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-04','YOU WILL BE THE FIRST BORN OF YOUR HOUSE','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Reuben, thou art my first born, my might, and the beginning of my strength, the Excellency of dignity, and the Excellency of power&rdquo; (Gen. 49.3)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOU WILL BE THE FIRST BORN OF YOUR HOUSE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I was discussing with a man recently, in the course of the discussion I ask him if he was the first bom of their house and he said to me yes. After which he told me that he has 3 elder ones before him; then I said, why did you call yourself the first born of your house? He said because I am the only person God blesses with wealth (the richest) among my father\'s children. I suddenly busted into laughter. I later pondered on what he said and the Holy Spirit said the man is correct, because he is doing the work of a first born even though biologically he is the fourth child of the father. God will make you so mighty that you will do more than your elder ones in Jesus name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You may be the least in your office, least in that your business, my God will give you overtaking speed that will qualify you to be the first born in your field in Jesus name. Wisdom Lime: (Divine favour can give you overtaking ability)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, give me your overtaking grace that will qualify me the first born anywhere I find myself. Make me mightier than anyone in my field.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2019-07-03 02:50:08'),(99,'DAILY FIRE..(4).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-05','YOU SHALL NOT BE CURSED','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Unstable as water, thou shall not excel because you went up to your father\'s bed; then thou defiled it. He went up to my couch&rdquo; (Gen. 49:4)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOU SHALL NOT BE CURSED</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Curse causeless shall not come. If anyone lay curse on you without any fault let me tell you it can never come to pass. Reuben was cursed by his father and the curse came to pass why because he did an accurse thing, when you do an abominable thing, get set for curse that will shatter your life. Sleeping with your sister is abomination, stealing God\'s money, cheating, fornication, adultery, speaking against the anointed one can bring you under a curse. If you don\'t want to lose your chances of greatness, run away from anything called abomination. Reuben lost his dignity, strength, power because he defiled his father&rsquo;s bed. That will not be your portion in Jesus mighty name. Live a righteous life and you will succeed in Jesus name. (Amen)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (There is no curse without a cause) Prayer: Father, help me to live a righteous life, let your grace be sufficient unto me. Let me not do what will make me incur curse upon my life. Thank you Jesus.</p>','2019-07-03 02:54:18'),(100,'DAILY FIRE..(5).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-06','DON\'T BE A BROTHER/SISTER TO A CRUEL PERSON','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Simeon and Levi are brothers; instruments of cruelty are in their habitation&rdquo; (Gen 49:5)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: DON\'T BE A BROTHER/SISTER TO A CRUEL PERSON</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Who is a cruel man/woman? A cruel man/woman is the one who takes pleasure in your suffering. Cruel person is the one who causes harm; a cruel person is a violence person. A cruel person can kill. Let\'s be careful the kind of people we move with. Is your friend a cruel person? If yes, quit that friendship, if not it will soon be your own turn, that same friend of yours will face you one day and deal with you the same way he has been using you against others.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They don\'t end up well, nothing like success in their records. Study the people around you after reading today\'s portion, carefully check and ponder on what your friends tell you, you will know if you are around cruel people or not. May God keep you away from them in Jesus name. (Amen)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Bad communication corrupts good Manner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, may I not be cruel, keep me away from a cruel man. Let them be far from me, keep my children from cruel people.</p>','2019-07-03 02:48:25'),(101,'DAILY FIRE..(6).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-07','DON\'T BE A PARTY TO EVIL PLANNERS','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Let not my soul enter their council; let not my Honour be united to their assembly&rdquo; (Gen. 49:6a)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: DON\'T BE A PARTY TO EVIL PLANNERS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Psalm 1:1 says &ldquo;Blessed is the man who walks not in the counsel of the ungodly, nor stands in the path of sinners, nor sits in the seat of the scornful. Evil planners are everywhere, we must be careful not to seat with them or walk with them. Whenever they see somebody succeeding the next thing they do is to get someone with them to carry out their evil intention. They can\'t do it alone, so they always look for people to team up with them so as to scatter what you are building. Be careful with such people, don\'t seat with them, don\'t be a party to that evil plan. Any counsel that is not of God given to you, don\'t take it, run away from them, sometimes they make you see that plan as if it is God\'s own, seek counsel from godly people before you accept any counsel, you will not be party to any evil plan in Jesus name. (Amen)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (When you team up with the wicked. You will partake in their judgment)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, may I never join evil planners, let me never partake in anything call evil. Send every evil person away from me in Jesus name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2019-07-03 02:49:22'),(102,'DAILY FIRE..(7).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-08','I REBUKE EVERY WICKED ANGER IN YOU','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;For in their anger they slew a man, and in their self will they hamstrung an ox&rdquo;(Gen. 49:6b)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OurFocus: I REBUKE EVERY WICKED ANGER IN YOU</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I said wicked anger because we have holy anger. Holy anger is the kind of anger you have when someone does something wrong that can lead him/her to hell. This anger diffuses within a short time while wicked anger is the kind of anger that sees something good and is angry. It does not just stop there, he goes ahead to do harm, including killingt.There are people that when they are angry nobody comes around them because they can harm, in fact, they don\'t forgive. Once you offend them they will never forgive you until they take vengeance. This people are terrible in their anger.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you in such condition when you are angry, you can do havoc; I rebuke that spirit of wicked anger in your life right now in Jesus name. I replace that wicked anger with holy anger in Jesus name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Wicked anger resides in the bosom of fools but he that is of patient spirit is wise)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Lay your hands on your head and be on your knees and say father, deliver me from wicked anger that comes into my heart, dwell in my heart reign in my heart. Thank you Jesus in Jesus name I pray.</p>','2019-07-03 02:56:07'),(103,'DAILY FIRE..(8).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-09','EVIL DOERS SHALL BE SCATTERED','<p>Text: &ldquo;Curse be their anger, for it is fierce; and their wrath, for it is cruel, I will divide them in Jacob and scatterthem in Israel&rdquo; (Gen. 49:7)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: EVIL DOERS SHALL BE SCATTERED</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is good news to the righteous and a very bad news to evil doers. Make sure you are not among the evil doers because there is a sword coming from above to cause commotion in their midst. They never believe anything can scatter them because of the covenant they had made within them, but my God is sending angel Michael right now to the camp of the evil doers to destroy and consume them by fire in Jesus name. Anywhere they are gathered against Refiners house, against the anointed servant of God, against your progress, I command them scattered in Jesus name. Praise God for scattering your enemies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (God will scatter any plan that is not in favour of His children)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, any gathering against me, against my family, against Refiners house, against our daddy and mummy scattered in Jesus name.</p>','2019-07-03 02:49:47'),(104,'DAILY FIRE..(9).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-10','YOU WILL BE PRAISED','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Judah, you are he whom your brothers shall Praise&rdquo; (Gen. 49:8a)<br />\r\nOur Focus: YOU WILL BE PRAISED<br />\r\nPraise God! Halleluiah, what an exciting word for you today? God\'s word says you will be praise. No one praises you for nothing, for you to be praise by men, means God has used you to affect their lives positively.<br />\r\nJudah was praised because he spoke against killing his brother Joseph. He suggested another better way instead of hurting or harming their brother. If only you will not engage yourself in anything that will hurt or harm your brother, if only you will save the life of someone from clanger today, your name shall be recorded in the book of great men of ourtime.<br />\r\nIf you want to make it in life, make sure you exempt yourself from evil. God will keep and guide your way in Jesus name. (Amen)<br />\r\nWisdom Lime: (Good praise comes from doing what is right<br />\r\nPrayer: Father, let my name be praised, let your grace be upon me to do good in Jesus mighty name I pray</p>','2019-07-03 03:26:21'),(105,'DAILY FIRE..(10).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-11','YOU WILL DOMINATE YOUR ENEMIES','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Your hand shall be on the neck of your enemies&quot; (Gen. 49:8b)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOU WILL DOMINATE YOUR ENEMIES</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enemies are people who don\'t like you. They hate to see your progress. They never pray for anything good to happen to you. They are always desperate to see you in pain. This morning such people shall be highly disappointed in your life. You will dominate them; God will put them in your hands. You will have choice to do whatever you like with them. All those who plan evil against you will surely be delivered to your hand one day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your hand will be on their neck. They will be helpless and you will decide what happen to them. No matter how long, evil doer will come back to your hands. I see God delivering your enemies to your hands soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Evil men must surely bow down to good men sooner or later)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, put my hands on the neck of my enemies. Let all those who plot evil against me come under my dominion in the name of Jesus Christ.</p>','2019-07-03 02:41:24'),(106,'DAILY FIRE..(11).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-12','YOU WILL RECEIVE THE GREATEST BLESSING','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Your father\'s children shall bow down before you&rdquo; (Gen. 49:8c)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOU WILL RECEIVE THE GREATEST BLESSING</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jacob blessed his children before he died but out of those blessings the greatest was given to Judah. He said to Judah you will be the greatest of all even though you are not the first born. The first born messed up and the blessing was transferred to Judah the younger brother. God said &ldquo;your father&rsquo;s children shall bow down before you&rdquo; which means you will be highly favoured than others, you will be the richest, you will be the wealthiest. No one will be as great as you in your family, oh what a great blessing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Released such blessings upon your life today in Jesus name. You may not look like it now, but God\'s overtaking grace will take you there in Jesus name. If only you will not go out of the will of God like Reuben did, this blessing will come to pass in your life in Jesus name. (Amen)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Favour offers you the greatest blessing even when you are the youngest)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, release the blessing of the first born upon me. Make me the greatest in my family, my blessing will not be transferred to anyone in Jesus name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2019-07-03 02:40:32'),(107,'DAILY FIRE..(12).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-13','I DECLARE YOU A LION','<p>OurText: &ldquo;Judah is a lion\'s whelp; from the prey, my son, you have gone up. He bows down; he lies down as a lion; and as a lion, who shall raise him? (Gen. 49:9)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: I DECLARE YOU A LION</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lion is an animal of great majesty and power, very courageous, fearless and commands respect amidst other animals, no one dares him, no animal dare come close to a lion. Finally, he is always victorious in his battles, I put in you the boldness of a lion. No one will be able to dare you. You will command respect anywhere you go in Jesus name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will fear no evil; evil will rather fear you just like other animal fear lion. You are untouchable to your enemies, no boss can sack you from work in Jesus name, this declaration will not elude you. Say thank you Jesus 3 times.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (When you are BOLD your enemies become COLD)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, I claim these declarations, let it work in me; make me untouchable to any principalities and powers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2019-07-03 02:43:08'),(108,'DAILY FIRE..(13).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-14','YOU WILL CONTINUE TO REIGN','<p>OurText: &ldquo;The sceptre shall not depart from Judah, nor a lawgiver from between his feet until Shiloh comes. And to him shall be the obedience of the people&rdquo; (Gen. 49:10)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOU WILL CONTINUE TO REIGN</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When a king is enthroned, he remains a king until death takes away his life. I have not seen any position like that of a king where it is only death that takes away the Position from you. That is the position God is taking you to. When you assume success, you will not stop getting money, it will not be said that you once have money but now you are wretched. Just like a king cannot be dethroned so shall your reign be in Jesus name. You will continue to reign forever. Jesus is another excellent example. He is the same yesterday, today and forever. Generation to come is still under Jesus. As you begin to reign, you will forever reign till Jesus comes in Jesus Name. (Amen)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (When you carry kingship grace, your reign will not be for a while)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, enthrone me forever, let me not be dethrone from something to nothing. Let the staff not depart from my hands.</p>','2019-07-03 02:41:03'),(109,'DAILY FIRE..(14).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-15','YOU WILL NOT WEEP','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Joseph threw himself on his father and wept overand kissed him&rdquo; (Gen.50:1-3)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOU WILL NOT WEEP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Be on your knees as you read through whatever will make you throw yourself on the ground, roll on the floor put your two hands on your head and screen like a mad person, I rebuke it over your life in the mighty name of Jesus Christ. Every plan of the devil to make you cry over someone precious to you in your family, I cancel it in Jesus name, that evil plan over your precious one has been transferred to your enemies family, instead of crying comes laughter, instead of mourning comes dancing, instead of sorrow comes joy and jubilation, say that is my portion in Jesus name. You will not go to the hospital to carry dead body, but to congratulate, says the LORD of host. Wisdom Lime: (The will of the devil is for you to weep while God\'s will is your joy, God\'s will is what I establish foryou)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Let me never see anything that will make me cry bitterly today in Jesus name I pray.</p>','2019-07-03 02:42:08'),(110,'DAILY FIRE..(15).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-16','YOUR TROUBLE IS OVER','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;And the period of mourning was over, Joseph approached Pharaoh\'s adviser and said, &ldquo;Please do me this favour and speak to Pharaoh on my behalf&rsquo; (Gen. 50:4)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOUR TROUBLE IS OVER</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the book of Eccl. 3:1 says, &ldquo;To everything there is a season, a time for every purpose under the heaven. A time to born, and a time to die, a time of war, and a time of peace, a time to mourn, and a time to dance&rdquo;. Your season of trouble is over; God is not an unjust God to forget the labour of your love. You can\'t continue in that trouble, this morning you are receiving a letter of divorce from that persistent trouble in your life in Jesus name. When there is trouble in your life, you can\'t have peace and when there is no peace in your life you can\'t enjoy sound health you can\'t move forward neither can you think right. Whatever is troubling your life I command in the name of Jesus receive liberty from it now! The season of trouble is over. Your season of freedom has come. Match into your victory.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (You are not destined to carry trouble all your life, it\'s time to drop your trouble for peace)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, enough is enough of my trouble, give me a letter of divorce from everything troubling my life. Thank you for my season of peace has come.</p>','2019-07-03 02:42:24'),(111,'DAILY FIRE..(16).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-17','YOUR FATHER WILL NOT DIE UNTIL HE HAS ENJOYED YOUR SUCCESS','<p><strong>O</strong>ur Text: &ldquo;My father made me swear saying&rdquo; Behold I am dying, in my grave which I dug for myself in the land of Canaan, there you shall bury me&rdquo; now therefore, please let me get up and bury my father and I will come back&rdquo; (Gen.50:5)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOUR FATHER WILL NOT DIE UNTIL HE HAS ENJOYED YOUR SUCCESS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I speak to someone this morning that got the information your father is very sick. Relax, I have a word for you, he will not die now, your father has not enjoyed your success yet, so it is forbidden for him to die now. Your father is permitted to die after he has over enjoyed your success. But for those of you that are still struggling to make it, I rebuke the grip of death on your father. Your father must see and eat of your success before his death.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I break the power of death over your dad this morning. He must not die until he enjoys your favour in life. Pray for your father and he must recover. He must not die until he taste your success. If you believe, then stand on this word and yourfather will live!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Death is allowed after your father has seen and eaten of your success)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Lord Jesus I pray for my father never to die now until he sees and taste of my success in life. I break the yoke of death on him. I command him to rise and be healed in the Mighty name of Jesus Christ.</p>','2019-07-03 02:41:50'),(112,'DAILY FIRE..(17).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-18','MASTER\'S FAVOUR','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;And Pharaoh said, &ldquo;Go up and bury your father, as he made you swear&rdquo; (Gen. 50:6)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: MASTER\'S FAVOUR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am speaking this morning to those of you that are under a master, be it government, NGO or private sector. God will grant you favour before your master in Jesus name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That request of yours, that you have tendered before your master and he is not showing concern about it, today marks the beginning of favour from your master in Jesus name. Tender that request again and it shall be granted. That application will be considered, there will be a favourable response for you. Don\'t bother about the number of times you tried and failed, try again, you will be highly favoured in Jesus name. Your long awaiting promotion has been effected. Give glory to God.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (When you are favoured your desires are gran ted before your master)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, let me secure my master\'s favour, let there be no hatred between us, thank you Jesus for in your mighty name I pray.</p>','2019-07-03 02:42:50'),(113,'DAILY FIRE..(18).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-20','YOUR ENTIRE HOUSEHOLD SHALL MOVE FORWARD','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Joseph also took his entire household and his brothers and their household. But they left their little children and flocks and herds in the land of Goshen&rdquo; (Gen. 50:8)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOUR ENTIRE HOUSEHOLD SHALL MOVE FORWARD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is a saying that says, &ldquo;One rich man in the midst of many poor men is a poor man.&quot;. Why? Because, their responsibilities are left for one man. This becomes so burdensome on him. When only one man in a family is rich, the riches may not show. In fact, if you are not careful you go backward, because the burden is too much for only one person. It is not design that way but when you have 3 rich men in a family often that is a good number the burden that only one man would have carried is being shared to three men. This year, you will not be the only one shouldering the responsibilities of your family. God will raise your entire family up in Jesus name. You may be the richest but you won\'t be the only rich man again in your family in Jesus name. (Amen)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (The higher the number of the progressive the better the family\'s welfare)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, raise my household up lift every member of my family higher, make my siblings rich in Jesus</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2019-07-03 02:43:45'),(114,'DAILY FIRE..(19).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-21','THERE SHALL BE A GREAT GATHERING','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;And there went up with him both chariot and horsemen, and it was a very great gathering&rdquo; (Gen.50:9) Our Focus: THERE SHALL BE A GREAT GATHERING</p>\r\n\r\n<p>God is about to do something wonderful, great, mighty and marvellous in your life that will call for a great gathering. An unexpected miracle is coming your way that very thing that you have long been waiting for or have lost hope on will suddenly come. This thing will attract men of timber and calibre, young and old, say amen if you believe. My wedding was a great gathering that attracted a lot of people because it was unexpected and surprising to me and many others. Great gathering that will call for celebration. I command it to come your way in Jesus Name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (When God performed a miracle for you. Many will gather to rejoice with you)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, do something that will attract many to celebrate with me this year.</p>','2019-07-03 02:44:07'),(115,'DAILY FIRE..(20).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-22','YOU WILL NOT MOURN NOW','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Then they came to the threshing flood of Atad which is beyond the Jordan, and they mourned there with a great and solemn lamentation. He observed seven days of mourning for his father&rdquo; (Gen.50:10)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOU WILL NOT MOURN NOW</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To mourn is to weep for a lost one. To have people gather at your house to sympathize with you. I cancel that for you today. You will not mourn over anyone now. No life will be lost today in your family. My God will keep you all. You will not weep. Death will not strike anyone in your domain. The Lord will protect you all. I reject mourning for you now. His covering shall be on you</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Loss of life bring about mourning while addition of life brings rejoicing, I cancel mourning for you)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, let me not have any reason to mourn today, Let your grace speak joy to my family this day in Jesus name I pray.</p>','2019-07-03 02:44:49'),(116,'DAILY FIRE..(21).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-23','GUILTY CONSCIENCE','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;When Joseph\'s brothers saw that their father was dead, they said perhaps Joseph will hate us, and may actually repay us for all the evil which we did to him&rdquo; (Gen.50:15)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: GUILTY CONSCIENCE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Joseph\'s brothers felt troubled in their spirit after their father&rsquo;s death. They thought Joseph would perhaps deal with them as their father was no more. Joseph never thought of that but their conscience disturbed them. When you do evil, you will certainly carry guilty conscience no matter how long. When you are an evil doer you will always believe people will harm you. You rarely have good thoughts. That is why evil does not pay, I do advise you this morning to avoid doing evil so your conscience can be cleared. Whenever you do evil to someone you don\'t find it easy to relate with that person freely. Even if the person forgives you, there is still some condemnation within your spirit. Evil brings torment to your conscience, withdraw from it and it shall be well with you in Jesus Christ name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Evil work will sentence your conscience to jail, avoid evil)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, break the grip of evil on my life so I would not carry guilty conscience all my life. Let there be liberty in my soul as I love everyone around me. (Amen)</p>','2019-07-03 02:45:05'),(117,'DAILY FIRE..(22).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-24','IT PAYS TO FORGIVE','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Thus shall ye say to Joseph; &ldquo;7 beg you please forgive the trespass of your brothers and their sin for they did evil to you and Joseph wept when they spoke to him&quot; (Gen.50:17)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: IT PAYS TO FORGIVE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Joseph\'s brothers realized their mistake and asked for his forgiveness Joseph wept when he remembered the magnitude of what they did to him, however he forgave them, I remember a young lady who had several frustrations attempting to travel abroad. Her VISA was rejected severally until the LORD told her to forgive her mother-in-law who offended her. As soon as she agreed and forgave her mother-in-law, her VISA was approved and she flew to join her husband abroad, unforgiveness can deny you a lot of favour, when you forgive you commit God to favour you in an unprecedented way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Forgiveness also makes you enjoy divine forgiveness. When you easily forgive people, God easily forgives your offenses too. When you find it difficult to forgive, God will also find it difficult to forgive you too. I must conclude with this truth, forgiveness becomes easy when the offender asks for forgiveness. If God does not forgive until we ask him to forgive our trespasses. So when you offend someone, kindly go to the person with all humility and ask him/her to please forgive and God will rant you favour. The manner of your presentation matters. Ask for forgiveness with all remorse and it would be easier for the person you offend to forgive you. Leam to forgive people that ask for it, don\'t be too rigid so God also can forgive you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (The more you easily forgive, the more God easily forgives you too.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, help me to forgive easily so I can enjoy your forgiveness too. Let me be merciful to those who ask for it so I can secure your mercy when I ask for it.</p>','2019-07-03 02:45:26'),(118,'DAILY FIRE..(23).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-25','GOD WILL PUT YOU IN A POSITION YOUR HATERS WILL BOW','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Then his brothers also went and fell down before his face, and they said &ldquo;Behold we are your servants&rdquo; (Gen. 50:18)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: GOD WILL PUT YOU IN A POSITION YOUR HATERS WILL BOW</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I learnt of some folks who treated President Goodluck Jonathan with disdain when he was the vice president. They never accorded honour to him as they were connected to the late president Yar&rsquo;adua. But mysteriously he became the President and those arrogant folks had no choice but to bow and accord him presidential honour. It is never their wish to do that but God enforced them. I foresee something similar about to happen to you. People who look down on you will have no choice but to bow down to you. God will put you in a position that will be highly honourable and all your haters will bow down to you. Whether they like you or not, God will enforce them to bow down for you. Shame shall cover their faces as they will be forced to respect you by the LORD. I rejoice with you in advance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (The best way to torment your enemies is for God to elevate you to the position they will bow to you)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, take me to a height all those who hate me will come and bow before me. Cover their faces with shame as they thought I will amount to nothing in Jesus Christ name I pray. (Amen)</p>','2019-07-03 02:46:07'),(119,'DAILY FIRE..(24).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-26','DONT BE AFRAID','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Joseph said to them, &ldquo;Do not be afraid (Gen. 50:19)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: DON\'T BE AFRAID</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I perceived someone woke up this morning with fear, perhaps, because of the bad dream you had overnight. Well the LORD sent me to you, He said I should tell you DON\'T BE AFRAID that evil dream is not your portion I cancel the effect on you in the Mighty Name of Jesus Christ. You will not experience that evil you saw in the dream. The LORD is with you, fear not.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The LORD sends me also to you who had a project that looks so scary. You are so afraid how you will go about it. The LORD of host says DON\'T BE AFRAID, I will help you through. I will give you the grace to accomplish it, rely on Him now you who is worried because of the state of your health. Why the worry? I am sent to inform you, that sickness is out of your body from today? Forget about the report you were given, hear God speaking to you this morning, you are healed of that DEADLY DISEASE! DONT BE AFRAID. Your healing is established in Jesus Mighty Name. Finally, those of you who are travelling today and you are lurked in fear, I destroy every force that wants to attack your vehicle. Your journey shall be safe; no evil will come your way. The LORD will grant you successful journey, you will not regret that trip so DON\'T BE AFRAID. It is a glorious day foryou.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Fear has dominion when God is not with you)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: I reject every trace of fear in my life today. I draw confidence in your presence that will go with me, no evil will come my way in Jesus Christ name I pray. (Amen)</p>','2019-07-03 02:46:40'),(120,'DAILY FIRE..(25).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-27','GOD WILL CHANGE EVERY EVIL PLANNED AGAINST YOU TO GOOD','<p>ur Text: &ldquo;But as for you, you meant evil against me but God meant it for good, in order to bring about as it is this day, to save many people alive&rdquo; (Gen. 50:20)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: GOD WILL CHANGE EVERY EVIL PLANNED AGAINST YOU TO GOOD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I remember a day I travelled. I was the first passenger in the car while I sat to wait for other passengers to arrive so the vehicle can be filled. I slept off on the chair beside the vehicle, when I woke up the vehicle was filled to the point someone even took over my seat. I complained he refused to leave the seat. I have to wait for the next vehicle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I felt disappointed because I had to wait for another one or two hours. Mysteriously God brought passengers in about 20 minutes and we left. On the way I saw the vehicle I boarded earlier had a fatal accident. The person that sat on my seat died instantly, I screamed when I saw the scene. It dawned on me how God turned the disappointment to deliverance for me. If God had not allowed them to disappoint me how would I have escaped that Death?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I pray for you this morning, every disappointment will work out deliverance for you. Any evil planned against you will work out to your advantage. Evil will be converted to good for you in Jesus Name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (If God is with you, evil is changed to blessings for you)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, convert every evil planned against me to a favour, let no wicked plan prevailed over my life ...in Jesus Name I pray.</p>','2019-07-03 02:47:05'),(121,'DAILY FIRE..(26).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-28','I WILL PROVIDE FOR YOU','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;Now therefore, do not be afraid; I will provide foryou and your little ones&rdquo; (Gen. 50:21a)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: I WILL PROVIDE FOR YOU</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I know you have a dare need this morning, there is something you earnestly need. Can you hear the voice of the LORD saying I WILL PROVIDE IT FOR YOU, You need not to be disturbed. The LORD will take care of your needs today. Great help will come your way this day. God will make a way for you where it looks impossible, don\'t cry anymore. He will provide for you. His hands are not too short to help you. A divine help will come your way today. My God has directed a mysterious supply for you today. So cheer up and thank him this morning. I see your help waiting foryou as you go out, it is WELL WITH YOU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (God will supply his help in your most pressing moment, there is help today foryou)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Thank you LORD for taking care of my needs today. My burdens are lifted as I welcome your help for my life today. (Amen)</p>','2019-07-03 02:47:23'),(122,'DAILY FIRE..(27).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-29','IT\'S YOUR DAY OF COMFORT','<p>Our Text: &ldquo;And he comforted them and spoke kindly to them&quot; (Gen.50:21b)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: IT\'S YOUR DAY OF COMFORT</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A brother I prayed for shared a testimony in our church of what God did after I prayed for him. He woke up one early morning to receive a call from his missing (lost) brother. For over nine years, they did not know his whereabouts. His mother died in the process of searching for him from pillar to post, it was a terrible experience. They concluded he was dead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, after the prayer of faith I prayed for him, I told them they will find him soon and God did that. The day he received the call from his missing brother, it was a day of GREAT COMFORT! It was refreshing and exciting, the thrill was alarming, to hear from someone they thought was dead. Now hear me, I prophesy to you today you will hear comforting news! Can you say your Amen louder! God will bring back what you thought was lost. You will obtain refreshing news this day. My God will do things that will bring comfort to your way today. It is a day of comfort for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (When the LORD shall comfort Zion we shall be as men that dream dreams)<br />\r\nPrayer: Oh Gracious Father, let me receive refreshing news as I go out today. Do something I would rarely believe and comfort me on every side. (Amen)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2019-07-03 02:45:49'),(123,'DAILY FIRE..(28).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-30','YOUR GOLDEN DREAM WILL COME TO PASS','<p>Our Text: &quot;And Joseph remember the dream which he dreamed of them, and said unto them, ye are spies to see the nakedness of the land ye are come. And they said unto him, nay my Lord, but to buy food are thy servants come&rdquo; (Gen.42.9)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: YOUR GOLDEN DREAM WILL COME TO PASS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What a joyful day this was for Joseph, to see his dream come to pass. All his brothers came to bow down before him and to buy com from him just as he dreamt it in the past. Every good dream you have had in the past will come to pass.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whatever the Lord has shown you before will come to pass one day. Whether the devil likes it or not, those great things the Lord has revealed to you must come to pass. As Joseph was not disappointed so you will not be disappointed. Your Good dreams will surely come to fulfilment. My God will honour all that he has shown you. You will travel to nations of the world to be a blessing just as it was shown to you in the past, it will come to pass in Jesus name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Every great vision of the past will come to pass)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, bring to pass all that you have revealed to me in the pass. Let me see those good dreams come to fulfilment in my life as you did it for Joseph, thank you, for you will do that forme in Jesus name.</p>','2019-07-03 02:44:28'),(125,'DAILY FIRE..(30).jpg','Jun - Jul (2019)','2019-07-31','THERE SHALL BE MIRACULOUS PROVISION FOR YOU','<p>Our Text: Gen 42:25 &ldquo;Then Joseph commanded to fill their sacks with corn, and to restore every man&rsquo;s money into his sack and to give them provision for the way: and thus did he unto Them.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Focus: THERE SHALL BE MIRACULOUS PROVISION FOR YOU Provisions are highly appreciated when they are desperately needed. In your point of desperation, the Lord will suddenly surprise you with great provision. There shall be a miraculous provision for you today. What is miracle? Miracle is a sudden, surprising and supernatural provision. What and where you don\'t expect, the Lord will get across to you. Joseph\'s brethren weren\'t expecting such provision but they received it. God will do likewise For you, something that will shock you will come your way; my God will fill your empty sacks with surprises today. You will have a miraculous sales today, miraculous patronage on your way this day, even when you think nothing will happen, the Lord will suddenly surprise you. For all of you that believe in the grace of God in my life, get ready for a miraculous provision today. You will experience God in action today, thank him in advance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wisdom Lime: (Miracles are sudden, surprising and supernatural provision to rescue you from emergency needs, you will experience miracles)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prayer: Father, grant me the miracles I urgently need to overcome all my obstacles. Let your divine provisions settle all my desperation that I may glorify you forever in Jesus name I pray. (Amen)</p>','2019-07-04 02:02:10');

