insert  into `daily_quotes`(`id`,`content`,`postedby`,`dateposted`) values (1,'Until the Kindgom of God becomes your 1st priority,u will never be free from the life of Worries as long as God is on TOP in ur life u won\'t STOP struggling in vain!\r\nExtract from Pst Faith Paul Empowerment Message today in Barnersville Montserrado\r\nIt was awesome in His Presence!','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-07-24 18:53:50'),(2,'<p>I decree an Encounter that will produce Shout of Joy in your life in ds Season of our Divine Encounter! Hear this U will MEET people that NEED U and U will MEET people Ur Life NEED. Ur Life will be a SEED to someone this Month and Someone will be a SEED 2U In the Mighty name of Jesus Christ. - Prophetic Blessing</p>','Pst. Faith. Joshua','2017-09-06 23:45:53'),(3,'<p>Prophetic Blessings: We decree u will Never Lack Bread and Wine of Joy in your life U will Rise above your Lacks Grace and mercy will provide all U Need in the Name of The LORD!</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-09-20 22:34:25'),(4,'<p>Do u know when Elijah declared Drought God told him to move to the Eastward and A RAVEN was commanded to feed him?1kgs17:1-7. That is what I called THE RAVEN CONNECTION A connection that will sustain u in CRUCIAL/CRITICAL MOMENT it\'s a short but VERY NEEDFUL Help. This week The LORD will connect U with a RAVEN That will give u TIMELY HELP to crush ur CRUCIAL NEEDS!</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-09-26 03:09:24'),(5,'<p>Celebration of FREEDOM right?<br />\r\nWhat is FREEDOM?<br />\r\nVery simple FREE 2 live in ur own DOMAIN<br />\r\nFREE +DOMAIN =FREEDOM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We decree anywhere u are held captive u are set FREE! Get to ur own DOMAIN and reign, however be FULLY ready to take RESPONSIBILITY for all ur actions both Positive and Negative FREEDOM without RESPONSIBILITY will end u in BOREDOM! Happy Independence Nigerians!</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-10-01 22:38:16'),(6,'<p>I DECREE Whatever The devil has stolen from u RESTORED, I DISMISS d devil over ur Life I render his enterprise Useless over ur Family. U are blessed beyond his reach in Jesus Mighty name!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prophetic Blessing from<br />\r\nSIERRA LEONE RESTORATION CRUSADE ON GOING WITH PASTOR FAITH AND PAUL S JOSHUA</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-10-13 05:22:34'),(7,'<p>There is a VALUE d devil loves to steal ie PATIENCE once he succeed in stealing this value he makes u do crazy things like Money rituals, stealing,taking someone\'s husband or consulting native doctors for help! Any help that has no God as it origin will entangle u. Be careful when u are running out of patience d devil can take advantage to make u do d Wrong Thing! I decree u will not lose d Value of Patience in ur life,whatever u have lost God\'s Mercy will help u Recover it Don\'t lose ur Patience, Wait, God is about to meet ur Needs!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Extracts from SIERRA LEONE RESTORATION CRUSADE ON GOING WITH PASTOR FAITH &amp; PAUL S JOSHUA</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-10-13 05:23:48'),(8,'<p>SIERRA LEONE RESTORATION CRUSADE ON GOING WITH PASTOR FAITH &amp; PAUL S JOSHUA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>THE CONSEQUENCES OF LOST OF VISION<br />\r\nBlind Bartemeaus case study Mark 10:46-52</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.Affliction<br />\r\n2.Begging<br />\r\n3.Confusion<br />\r\n4.Division</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once u lose ur Vision u have sign in for Affliction, Begging,Confusion and A Divided or shattered life<br />\r\nShow me a Man without Vision I will tell u u have seen a man of Confusion and Division!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Saviour of any Family MUST BE Men of VISION,Families without VISIONARY will b subject to Bankruptcy &amp; Begging</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is either u get ur Vision back or u remain a Beggar d rest of ur life. If u don\'t have a clear chat of where u are going in life,u are subject to lack of vision, Request Ur Vision back, The God of Mercy is willing to help u and ur Story will change from Sorry to Glory!</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-10-13 05:26:25'),(9,'<p>There is a VALUE d devil loves to steal ie PATIENCE once he succeed in stealing this value he makes u do crazy things like Money rituals, stealing,taking someone\'s husband or consulting native doctors for help!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any help that has no God as it origin will entangle u. Be careful when u are running out of patience d devil can take advantage to make u do d Wrong Thing!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I decree u will not lose d Value of Patience in ur life,whatever u have lost God\'s Mercy will help u Recover it Don\'t lose ur Patience, Wait, God is about to meet ur Needs!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Extracts from SIERRA LEONE RESTORATION CRUSADE ON GOING WITH PASTOR FAITH &amp; PAUL S JOSHUA</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-10-13 05:28:07'),(10,'<p>When MERCY is at work on ur behalf God never REMEMBER,RETAIN OR REFLECT on your Mess. Once Mercy SPEAKS,JUDGMENT &amp; ITS CONSEQUENCES Stay STILL. Today Mercy will Speak for Someone and Judgment will be Silenced forever in ur Case. Shout Mercy will Speak for me!!!!!!!!</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-10-24 13:07:00'),(11,'<p>A Wise Man don\'t see The FAULT in his spouse but The SALT in Her; Stop Condemning ur Spouse Start Commending &amp; Check The result u will get!<br />\r\nWisdom Lime by Paul S Joshua</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-10-24 13:07:50'),(12,'<p>Whatever u Tolerate remains,until u Enforce a change some circumstance will never change on their own accord. Whatever u don\'t like in ur life Do Something about it and Stop Pitying Yourself, God needs ur Spiritual Aggression on some issues to help d Implementation of Divine Change. Right now Think of 3 Things u hate to see in ur life and begin to Shout I TEAR AND CRUSH U OUT OF MY LIFE BY POWER IN THE NAME OF JESUS!!!!!GO ahead and TEAR whatever u hate in ur life as Blind Bartemeous tear his garment of Begging! I see u Dancing Soon for a Great Restoration taking place in ur life!</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-10-26 04:31:00'),(13,'<p>When U are Most Depressed U need to be in God\'s House for STRENGTH.When U are also Highly Excited u need to be There to express ur Gratitude! Never sit in ur House when u should be in His House or Satan will seat in ur house!Do u want d devil to sit in ur house? If no,Get Prepared.</p>','Pst. Paul S. Joshua','2017-10-29 23:30:41');

