insert  into `resourses`(`id`,`image`,`product_details`,`product_name`,`price`,`vid_code`,`amazon`) values (3,'Amazon_Cover.jpg','THE GLIMPSE\r\nYOUR DREAMS AND ITS INTERPRETATION is o book written under the inspiration of the Holy Spirit to interpret and expose meanings to your dreams! It equips you with divine knowledge, empowering you to escape evil agenda.\r\nWhen you dream seeing yourself\r\n*Stranded or wondering on a field or bush\r\n*Standing naked in the dream\r\n*Stabbed or shot with a gun in the dream\r\n*Swimming in the dream\r\n*Standing, sitting and speaking with dead people in the dream\r\n*Seeing money in the dream\r\n*Having sex in the dream\r\n*Seeing Snakes and dogs in the dream 4 Fighting in the dream\r\n*Seeing masquerade in the dream 4 Seeing dwarf in the dream\r\n*Seeing two she-goats tied together in the dream\r\n*Crying in the dream\r\n*In an old school writing exam in the dream\r\nDo not fake these revelations lightly. Find out how the Holy Spirit will have you tackle them. Get blessed as you read on, and be ready to receive your deliverance from Horrific Dreams by His grace!\r\nABOUT THE AUTHOR\r\nPAUL S. JOSHUA is on Apostle, Prophet, Dynamic, Teacher, Seasoned Counselor as well on ANOINTED INGENIOUS Dream Interpreter. His popular Radio and Telecast â€˜YOUR DREAMS AND ITS INTERPRETATIONâ€™ blesses many lives tremendously across Lagos. Nigeria. Africa and the entire Globe.\r\nHe is the Senior Pastor of The Refiner\'s House Ministry with the focus of Empowering Men with Right Values and to raise People of Power & Performance in Christ He is The Director of The Refiner\'s School of Ministry (RESOM) where Powerful leadersâ€™ ore raised. He is based in Lagos with other branches across Nigeria. He has passion for the Needy. He is married to Faith Modupe Paul {President ZION TALENTS SHOW INITIATIVES - a popular TV Program). She also pastors with him. They are blessed with four (4) wonderful children.','YOUR DREAMS AND ITS INTERPRETATION','1000','57bf0ab59ad3a','https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B07CGHXYVP'),(5,'IMG-20180425-WA0004.jpg','WISDOM EMBASSY is a vault of treasure, a book written under divine inspiration with liberating power as you diligently apply its wisdom. Hear this counsel! \"Go to the ant, thou sluggard; consider her ways and be wise: which having no guide, overseer, or ruler, provideth her meat in the summer, and gathereth her food in the harvest\". Pr. 6:6-8.Sought counsel from wise men and expand your horizon! What stands you out and distinguishes you as a Principal person in life is your ability to \"Cry out for insight, and ask for understanding. Search for them as you would for silver; seek them like hidden treasures. Tlien you will understand what it means to fear the Lord, and you will gain knowledge of God. For the Lord grants wisdom! From his mouth come knowledge and understanding. Fie grants a treasure of common sense to the honest. He is a shield to those who walk with integrity\".Pr.2:3-7.\r\nNever underrate the result you will get from the application of divine wisdom, it distinguishes you and possesses the potential to promote you beyond human reasoning.Yes! It is worth it, spare an hour or two of your time to read this book. I assure you, you will be glad you did.\r\n','Wisdom Embassy','1000','5b0f648ec4155','https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B07CGHXYVP'),(6,'IMG-20180329-WA0001.jpg','\"...For he is like a refiner\'s fire and like fuller\'s soap...â€ Mal.3:2\r\nIt is a wonderful, sparkling and energizing daily devotional guide, designed to empower your day with the Right values. It was written under divine Guidance and I can assure you whatever you will read on each day will just be the exact fire you need for the day!\r\nItâ€™s written with all simplicity and brevity to enable you meet all day\'s schedules. Just a few verses of the word and the light in it. with a prayer point associated to what you read, and then you are set for your day\'s success. If you have a family, read it together and pray the prayer for the day together.\r\nYou will enjoy this year more than any year of the past. 2018 OUR YEAR OF DIVINE TRANSFORMATION Get set, as you enjoy each day through this daily fire guide.\r\n		\r\nABOUT THE AUTHOR\r\nPAUL S. JOSHUA is an Apostle, Prophet, Dynamic Teacher, Seasoned Counselor as well an ANOINTED INGENIOUS Dream Interpreter. His popular Radio and Telecast â€™YOUR DREAMS AND ITS INTERPRETATION\' blesses many lives tremendously across Lagos, Nigeria. Africa and the entire Globe.\r\nHe is the Senior Pastor of The Refinerâ€™s House Ministry with the focus of Empowering Men with Right Values and to raise People of Power & Performance in Christ. He is The Director of The Refiner\'s School of Ministry (RESOM) where Powerful Leaders are raised. He is based in Lagos with other branches across Nigeria. He has passion for the Needy\r\nHe is married to Faith Modupe Paul (President, ZION TALENTS SHOW INITIATIVES-a popular TV Program). She also pastors with him. They are blessed with four (4) wonderful children.\r\n+234703 795 3305, +234803 440 0914 \r\nEmail:refinershousekb@yahoo.com \r\npauljoshua@therefinershouse.com\r\nwww.facebook.com/refinershouse\r\nTwitter: @paulandfaithâ€ƒ','DAILY FIRE APRIL TO MAY 2018','200','5b0f5c4518739','https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B07CGHXYVP');

