insert  into `testimonies`(`id`,`verify`,`username`,`fname`,`lname`,`email`,`phone_no`,`title`,`limitedtextarea`,`dateposted`) values (1,'Verified',NULL,'BERNARD U.','KALU',NULL,'080xxxxxx','This ministry has also branded me spiritually, financially and materially.','<p>I must begin by giving glory to the Almighty God who has given Grace to his servant pastor Paul S. Joshua and faith Joshua over the Ministry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I wonder what my life would have been without this ministry. Through this ministry God has made me to be a carrier of DIPLOMA through this Refiner\'s Academy. This ministry has also branded me spiritually, financially and materially.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I also thank God for making me know all it takes to be a good minister and the charisma and character that go with it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I finally want to thank God for given me all it takes to run a good home through the help of this ministry, and the Lord has given me an inner eye to know what I couldn&rsquo;t have known ordinance.</p>','2017-09-20 01:08:39'),(2,'Verified',NULL,'DORCAS','UTEE',NULL,'080xxxxxx1','This ministry training has reformed my life in several ways.','<p>This ministry training has reformed my life in several ways, I am very happy to be part of the trainees, I would have continued in darkness. No wonder the Bible says, seek ye first the kingdom of God and his righteousness and every other thing shall be added unto you. The following are some of the benefits to mention but just a few:<br />\r\n1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;It has widened or broaden; my scope of understanding in the word of God.<br />\r\n2.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;I now know that as a minister you have to live a life worth emulation and to serve people not for you to be served. Where I was coming from, the ministers re served, ruling, in short, so autocratic.<br />\r\n3.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;As a good minister, you must be able to change or transform people around you and feel what they feel.</p>','2017-09-20 01:10:36'),(3,'Verified',NULL,'KENNETH','AMEH',NULL,'080xxxxxx','l am no longer confused and I pursue my goals passionately.','<p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;l am no longer confused and I pursue my goals passionately.<br />\r\n2.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;lama better manager, I am always punctual and I utilized my time properly.<br />\r\n3.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;I comport myself very well knowing that my lifestyle could affect others positively or negatively.<br />\r\n4.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;I pray withe:&gt;t struggling and enjoy praying for people.<br />\r\n5.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;I am a better father and husband. I am more conscious of the needs of my family<br />\r\n6.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;I live a life of giving sacrificially to the needy, my time and money.<br />\r\n7.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;I know that I should practice what I preach.</p>','2017-09-20 01:11:40'),(4,'Verified',NULL,'IFEANYI','NDUBUEZE',NULL,'080xxxxxx','The training has enable me to see better and work harder for the house of God.','<p>MY EXPERIENCE<br />\r\nThe training has enable me to see better and work harder for the house of God. l am more determined to contribute to the progress of the house of God than ever.<br />\r\nI thank God and God\'s servant for given me the opportunity to be part of the refiner\'s Academy.<br />\r\nMy life has really changed. Praise God!</p>','2017-09-20 01:13:01'),(5,'Verified',NULL,'Gabriel','Abiodun Ojo',NULL,'080xxxxxx','I came to understand that man is originated from God','<p>From the basic ministry training I came to understand that man is originated from God, it is not just an accidental creation as philosophy says man is from Ape. Again from this academy I was empowered with the knowledge of the factors that influence man; the factor of tradition, custom and beliefs, the force of philosophy and wrong peer group.In ministry analysis I got the understanding that ministers are called by God to carry out certain ministerial functions.</p>','2017-09-20 01:15:12'),(6,'verified','boro43','Adetoro','Celestine','ayocelest